oracion: Additionally, I will work with President Kapelou's office to restructure the allocation of funds from current gas and oil taxes to provide for rural health projects."

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Riot
oracion: POK members held a large demonstration in Abila yesterday.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Riot
oracion: Several dozen of their supporters held sit-ins in front of the capitol building and the presidential manor, while others took to the streets with their signs and chants.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Riot
oracion: Police called for the peaceful end to the sit-ins, but were answered with a barrage of rocks and bottles from the crowd.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Riot
oracion: The violence escalated into a full blown riot and police were forced to use tear gas, pepper spray, water cannons, and beanbags shot from shotguns to control the crowd.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Riot
oracion: By the time the crowds finally dispersed, several government buildings had been vandalized, two police vehicles were ablaze, and the streets were littered with trash and broken glass.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Riot
oracion: Several protestors and police were injured, including one heroic police officer who was stabbed by a crazed protestor.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Construction
oracion: President Araullo announced today that his government is planning the construction of a new, modern Abila General Hospital.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Construction
oracion: The old Abila General Hospital, built in 1930, has outdated health care facilities and has suffered numerous electrical fires in the past decade.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Construction
oracion: Hospital Administrator Torsten Trucco lauded the government's action saying, "We've been trying to get funding to update our facilities for years, to no avail.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Construction
oracion: Additionally, it will have a full emergency services area, trauma and burn care units, a psychiatric care wing, and four ultra-modern surgical suites.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Construction
oracion: In his announcement of the new construction, Araullo said, "Our strategy of courting foreign investment is paying great dividends.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Construction
oracion: This new hospital is the first of many projects we plan to pursue to help upgrade our standard of living and modernize our lifestyle."

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Again
oracion: POK members held their annual demonstration in Abila yesterday.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Again
oracion:
A larger than usual crowd gathered in front of the Capitol building, waving signs holding pictures of Elian Karel and Juliana Vann, who were painted as POK "martyrs".   

Police and government security forces set up between the protestors and the Capitol building in a show of force, hoping to prevent the kind of chaos that occurred during last year's riot.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Again
oracion: However, after several hours of chanting and speeches, tempers in the crowd flared and protestors rushed the police line.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Again
oracion: The police forces were forced to use tear gas, pepper spray, water cannons, and rubber bullets to subdue the crowd and protect property.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Again
oracion: In spite of their heroic efforts, the protestors managed to break some windows, damage several police vehicles, and injure three officers.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrests
oracion: Dozens of protesters attending a Protectors of Kronos (POK) rally in front of the GAStech regional headquarters in Abila were arrested for trespassing this morning.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrests
oracion: The POK rally was intended to draw attention to their claims of environmental damage being caused by the development of gas and oil fields around Kronos by foreign corporations like GAStech.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrests
oracion: About two hundred people gathered in front of the GAStech building chanting slogans and waving signs that held the visages of people who have allegedly died due to environmental contamination.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrests
oracion: Ten of the protestors chained themselves to the doors of the building in an attempt to prevent GAStech employees from going to work.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrests
oracion: Police spokesman Adrien Carman said, "We allowed the group some latitude with their rally, but when GAStech complained that the protestors were blocking entrance to their building, we had to take action.  Government spokesman Rufus Drymiau said of today's POK rally, "We have been concerned by a pattern of increasingly aggressive tactics by the Protectors of Kronos for some time now.

titulo: Grand Opening of the New GAStech Offices
oracion: President Sten Sanjorge Jr.

titulo: Grand Opening of the New GAStech Offices
oracion: The gleaming steel and glass building provides ample office space for regional managers, geologists, engineers, and support staff, and sports state-of-the art conference facilities.

titulo: Grand Opening of the New GAStech Offices
oracion: Minister Sarto, who attended the celebration, said, "This beautiful facility is a monument to Sanjorge's commitment to Kronos and should be seen by the citizens as a sign of a prosperous future for all."

titulo: POK Assault Police in Abila
oracion: Police spokesman Adrien Carmen informed the media today that members of the POK assaulted a police patrol in Abila early this morning.

titulo: POK Assault Police in Abila
oracion: The POK thugs crept up on two patrol officers who were sitting in their vehicle and ambushed the men, bashing the windows of their car and dragging them out of the vehicle into the street.

titulo: POK Assault Police in Abila
oracion: The criminals then proceeded to deface the car with spray-painted POK logos.

titulo: POK Assault Police in Abila
oracion: "Assaulting a police officer and destroying government property are serious crimes," Carmen said.

titulo: Government Announces Tax Incentives For Foreign Investment
oracion: Today the Parliament voted 86 to 14 in favor of President Araullo's package of tax incentives designed to lure foreign investment to our fair country.

titulo: Government Announces Tax Incentives For Foreign Investment
oracion: The tax incentives specifically target energy development companies, which the government hopes to lure to Kronos' rich, but yet undeveloped, gas fields.

titulo: Government Announces Tax Incentives For Foreign Investment
oracion: Ministry of the Interior projections show that development of just the Tiskele Bend fields could bring in as many as 5,000 high paying jobs and yield billions of dollars of infrastructure development over the next 20 years.

titulo: GAStech and Kronos Celebrate Partnership
oracion: Local GAStech executives Ingrid Barranco, Ada Campo-Corrente, Orhan Strum, and Willem Vasco-Pais will attend a reception with government officials tomorrow following a business meeting at their headquarters building.

titulo: GAStech and Kronos Celebrate Partnership
oracion: Government spokesman Rufus Drymiau informed The Star that Sten Sanjorge Jr., President and CEO of GAStech, has traveled from Tethys to attend the events.

titulo: GAStech and Kronos Celebrate Partnership
oracion: The reception, hosted by President Kapelou at the Capitol Building, is being held to celebrate the 20th year of cooperation between the corporation and our country.

titulo: GAStech and Kronos Celebrate Partnership
oracion: Taxes paid by GAStech have funded many infrastructure improvements including projects such as the modernization of Abila General Hospital, numerous schools, and hundreds of miles of paved highways.

titulo: POK Labeled a "Public Threat"
oracion: In a statement to the press today, government spokesman Rufus Drymiau said of the POK: "they are justifiably a public threat due to violent demonstrations, opportunistic vandalism, and clashes with the police."

titulo: POK Labeled a "Public Threat"
oracion: Violence and vandalism have become a trademark of POK gatherings lately.

titulo: POK Labeled a "Public Threat"
oracion: "They have caused thousands of dollars in damage to buildings and businesses, showing they have little care for the plight of the people.

titulo: Tiskele Bend Gas Fields Larger Than First Thought
oracion: A press release from the Ministry of Interior today announced that the Tiskele Bend gas fields could be as much as 5 times larger than originally estimated.

titulo: Tiskele Bend Gas Fields Larger Than First Thought
oracion: When we contacted Minister Sarto's office for comment, he said, "We were astounded by the results of GAStech's recent survey of Tiskele Bend.

titulo: Tiskele Bend Gas Fields Larger Than First Thought
oracion: We have already undertaken several large improvement projects like the port expansion and the new hospital that we would not otherwise have been able to do because of the taxes we are seeing from our foreign investments.

titulo: Tiskele Bend Gas Fields Larger Than First Thought
oracion: This news almost assures we'll be able to reap those same dividends for decades to come!"

titulo: Tiskele Bend Gas Fields Larger Than First Thought
oracion: One hopes that those who had been so shortsighted as to oppose his plan have finally come to their senses.

titulo: Activists Disrupt Traffic Near Tiskele Bend Fields
oracion: Five young people were arrested yesterday for protesting near the entrance to the Tiskele Bend fields as they called for government action to address their environmental concerns about GAStech's operations at the site.

titulo: Activists Disrupt Traffic Near Tiskele Bend Fields
oracion: The protestors, members of the activist group "Protectors of Kronos", held signs reading: "Drilling Poisoned Our Water" and "Remember Juliana", referring to 10 year old Juliana Vann, who has become an icon for the Protectors of Kronos since her death in 1998.

titulo: Activists Disrupt Traffic Near Tiskele Bend Fields
oracion: The protestors were arrested after one young man threw his sign at a government vehicle, cracking its window and startling the occupants.

titulo: Activists Disrupt Traffic Near Tiskele Bend Fields
oracion: Police spokesman Adrien Carman said of the arrests, "We decided to shut the protest down before the POK members escalated to further violence.

titulo: Activists Disrupt Traffic Near Tiskele Bend Fields
oracion: "The people of Kronos have overwhelmingly been for the development of our natural resources and all have benefited from the resultant economic growth.

titulo: Activist Leader Karel Arrested for Tax Evasion
oracion: Kronos police arrested Elian Karel today on charges of tax evasion.

titulo: Activist Leader Karel Arrested for Tax Evasion
oracion: Karel, the leader of the activist group "Protectors of Kronos", was conducting a meeting with his supporters when he was arrested.

titulo: Activist Leader Karel Arrested for Tax Evasion
oracion: Karel's lawyer, Michale Kraft, released a statement declaring that the charges against his client were false and that he hoped to have Karel released from police custody by week's end.

titulo: Activist Leader Karel Arrested for Tax Evasion
oracion: It is clear that Elian Karel, who professes to have the interests of the people of Kronos at heart, must explain to us why he refuses to contribute to the welfare of his nation.

titulo: Kapelou Calls POK "A Gang of Criminals"
oracion: In a press release today, President Kapelou today called the POK "a gang of criminals, thugs, and malcontents who have become a pestilence to our peaceful way of life."

titulo: Kapelou Calls POK "A Gang of Criminals"
oracion: President Kapelou has called for increased police patrols of the Elodis area and has said that all future POK demonstrations will be "met with maximum police force."

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarters
oracion: A Protectors of Kronos demonstration was held in front of Abila police headquarters yesterday morning.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarters
oracion: The POK had gathered in memorialize their former leader, Elian Karel, who died of natural causes in jail last year.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarters
oracion:
POK supporters carried signs with pictures of Karel and Juliana Vann, chanted slogans, and lit candles.  

The peaceful demonstration turned violent when two POK members accosted a man who attempted to enter the building on business.  The POK members hit him with a bottle, which knocked him to the ground and gave him a bloody gash on his forehead.  Abila police attempted to gain control of the situation by using bullhorns to call for the peaceful dispersal of the crowd, but the crowd responded to their calls by hurling insults along with a few rocks at the officers.  Police used tear gas to end the gathering, but a handful of die-hard POK members urged the crowd into melee with the officers.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarters
oracion: When the tear gas finally cleared, six POK member were arrested on charges of assault on civil authorities and inciting a crowd to violence.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarters
oracion: Marek replaced Elian Karel as the popular figurehead of the POK movement last summer.

titulo: Police Hold News Conference on GAStech Kidnapping
oracion: The Abila police held a press conference at nine this morning on the kidnapping GAStech headquarters.

titulo: Police Hold News Conference on GAStech Kidnapping
oracion:
Police informed reporters that four of the GAStech employees whose whereabouts were unconfirmed yesterday were found overnight, leaving ten people who are presumed missing. 

Police spokesman Adrien Carman said Tethyn federal law enforcement agencies are assisting in the investigation.  The POK rhetoric has become increasingly anarchist and their actions more criminal and violent over the past several years.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: The world of gas is distant, difficult and far flung.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: In Tethys a few years ago, I journeyed laboriously to the remote gas fields of Tethys to look at a contentious new energy producing area.

oracion: One of the sites I visited was a local office of the Sanjorge Gas company, crammed with reinforced work boots and overalls and the chemicals and supplies you need to run a gas operation.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: As I remember it, a former trucker was in charge.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: It was a vivid example of how a once small exploration company from Thethys had begun to grow into a mighty international force in the energy industry.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: But I'd forgotten about the encounter until I went back to Tethys the other day for the first time since their early years, to reacquaint with the man who created the business, Sten Sanjorge: one man (one of the richest individuals in Tethys) who has lived through the whole story of gas prospecting and prospered mightily from it.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: But as I went round the capital city of Centrum interviewing people, I soon realised that this was not just a story of new energy.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: Something very significant has happened to turn Centrum into a global centre of gas industry expertise.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry

oracion:

oracion: It then seemed a pretty impossible dream, turning an island of coal into a place with abundant oil and gas supplies.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry

oracion: Much to his mother's regrets, meanwhile, Sten Sanjorge had started prospecting in the early 1960s.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: The change in Centrum has been substantial.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: Sanjorge has recently started paying more attention to leisure activities and philanthropy, allowing his son Sten Jr. and co-founder Hank Fluss to run the company.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: But Sanjorge has just been asked to produce a report for the Tethan government recommending the best ways of ensuring that Tethys continues to produce energy for decades to come.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: The easy-to-get stuff has been produced, so keeping the gas coming will need much investment and more clever new techniques, such as the hyper-acidic substrate removal techniques developed by the company in 1974.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: So thanks to clever people such as Sten Sanjorge and the people who work with him, Centrum has achieved what every place where raw materials are discovered longs to do.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: The city has taken the temporary boon of energy on its doorstep, and turned it into specialized knowledge and intellectual property which may make Centrum a centre of gas expertise long after the gas itself runs out.

oracion: It has created towns and cities to service its operations, which it manages and runs almost single-handed.

oracion: The head of GAStech, Sten Sanjorge, Jr, whose photo stares out from calendars and picture frames everywhere in the country, acknowledges the "state within a state" accusations, but argues that the company simply needs to look after its workers and the communities around them.

oracion: Of course, people need good reasons to come and work in the hostile remote Kronosian regions.

oracion: They are provided with medical care, entertainment, and food.

oracion: The GAStech empire owns 2 thousand cows and 3 thousand pigs in its company farms, runs gyms, and offers subsidised holidays in Black Sea resorts for key employees.

oracion: It's there to serve the company's will.

oracion: It hardly seems the picture of a modern global company, as most of those have unceremoniously dumped their "non-core activities".

oracion: There is an argument, however, that the energy business is different from other industries, requiring energy corporations to operate in distinct ways.

oracion: Working in far-off places with no previous infrastructure means oil and gas sites will always be, to some extent, company towns.

oracion: GAStech certainly strives to ensure its employees can move in and out of these locations by operating a private fleet of four planes to ferry its staff the huge distances between sites.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: With the third anniversary of Elian Karel's death approaching - former member of the Protectors of Kronos - the question is: who are the protesters?

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: But not only who are they, what and why are they protesting?

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The Protectors of Kronos or POK were founded in 1997 by residents of rural Elodis on the advice of the now defunct Wellness for All (WFA), an international water safety group.
organizaciones: The Protectors of Kronos,POK,Wellness for All,WFA

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK was initiated to bring attention to the clean water issues surrounding Elodis to the Government of Kronos and the world.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK asserts that GAStech International's Tiskele Bend natural gas drilling site is the source of both the contamination of drinking water as well as the destruction of the traditional farmland surrounding Elodis.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: In 1998, WFA performed testing on the water of Elodis finding high levels of benzene, toluene and xylene arsenic, barium, chromium, lead and selenium.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The testing a subsequent statement released by WFA brought international attention and pressure on the government and GAStech to act.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: However, with the fragmenting of WFA due to funding issues, the POK's demands were largely ignored and downplayed.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: Also in 1998, Juliana Vann, a previously healthy ten-year old girl died of a lingering illness, which WFA-funded doctors claimed was caused by water contamination.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The Government of Kronos officially refuted the claim citing the fragmentation of the WFA organization as evidence of an unreliable source not to be trusted.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: Regardless, Juliana became the POK's first martyr and has used Juliana's image on campaign literature ever since.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK's second major martyr is Elian Karel, who died in 2009 while incarcerated of undetermined causes.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK asserts he was arrested on trumped up charges while the Government of Kronos contends he was a radical and violent activist engaged in tax evasion.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: Karel had been involved with the POK since its inception given that his father, Jeroen Karel, was an original member.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: Elian Karel's death in 2009 was marked by spontaneous instances of protest around Abila.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The anniversary of his death, June 19, has seen additional protests, demonstrations, riots, and violence.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK has evolved from peaceful protests and demonstrations demanding government action to more violent activities including riots as they claim that the government has done little to nothing in addressing the contamination, poisonings, and deaths suffered by their people.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: As of 2011, the Government of Kronos has labeled the POK as a "public threat".

titulo: TISKELE BEND EXPLOSION AND FIR
oracion: A spark at the GAStech International-owned well at the Tiskele Bend site ignited methane gas several hundred feet underground, causing a fireball and fire that burned for about an hour is the findings from a dual GAStech - government investigation of the explosion and subsequent fire Sunday morning.

oracion: In contrast to previous reports there were no deaths and none missing as a result of the incident.

titulo: TRAFFIC ACCIDENT NEAR ELODIS
oracion: Carmine Edris, 9, was found wandering around the accident site.

titulo: TRAFFIC ACCIDENT NEAR ELODIS
oracion: He succumbed to his injuries later at the Abila Hospital.

titulo: TRAFFIC ACCIDENT NEAR ELODIS
oracion: The GAStech truck driver received minor injuries and was taken to hospital for observations.

titulo: TRAFFIC ACCIDENT NEAR ELODIS
oracion: In a show of corporate largesse GAStech International vows to donate money to the remaining family members.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 1947 UPDATE -

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: From the Abila Police news conference: "There are approximately fourteen individuals unaccounted for among the GAStech staff.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: It has not yet been determined if all of these individuals are in fact missing."

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Though it was confirmed that over a dozen individuals were unaccounted for, the Abila Police said that that does not mean they are necessarily missing.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Nor does it mean that they have been abducted.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: At this point the case is under investigation and more information will be released as facts are learned.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: The Abila Police stressed that anyone seeing any unusual activity should immediately report it.

titulo: LANDSLIDE VICTORY FOR PRESIDENT KAPELO
oracion: The people of Kronos have overwhelmingly elected new President Dorel Kapelou II.

titulo: LANDSLIDE VICTORY FOR PRESIDENT KAPELO
oracion: Former President Luis Araullo conceded defeat yesterday when early returns came in strong for Kapelou II.

titulo: LANDSLIDE VICTORY FOR PRESIDENT KAPELO
oracion: Today marks a new dawn for the people of Kronos and a bright path forward for the country.

titulo: LANDSLIDE VICTORY FOR PRESIDENT KAPELO
oracion: The results for the 1 October election are as follows: Dorel Kapelou II elected with 62% of the vote and Luis Araullo receiving just 36% of the vote.

titulo: LANDSLIDE VICTORY FOR PRESIDENT KAPELO
oracion: A resounding victory for the new elected President and a clear mandate for Kapelou's vision for the country.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 1506 UPDATE -

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Police have begun to leave GAStech headquarters.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: The officers have declined to answer all of the reporters' questions leaving the scene.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: A few police vehicles have remained behind.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Presumably the remaining officers are interviewing the GAStech employees who still remain inside the company's building.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: The police cordon still remains around the GAStech building.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 2021 UPDATE -

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: A Kronos Government official who asked not to be identified but was present at the government reception has gone on the record stating, "Investigators are working around the clock to ensure that the kidnapped GAStech employees are found and that the perpetrators are brought to justice."

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: LOCATION:

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: This is the first confirmation that today's events surrounding GAStech

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: This is the first confirmation that today's events surrounding GAStech - Kronos are in fact a kidnapping.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: With fourteen individuals still unaccounted for, at this point, the assumption is that all are the victims of a kidnapping.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: No group has come forward yet to claim responsibility nor have any demands been made.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 1732 UPDATE -

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Much of the information gathered from the GAStech employees who have been allowed to leave by police investigators point to a kidnapping of several GAStech employees.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: However, officials still have not confirmed a kidnapping has taken place.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: The number of missing employees is undetermined at this time given the earlier confusion with the false fire alarm.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: There is some indication that the Protectors of Kronos - an activist group responsible for many recent demonstrations and riots in and around Abila - are suspected of being responsible for the kidnapping.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: If true, this is an alarming escalation of violence for the activist group.

titulo: POK LEADER ARRESTE
oracion: Elian Karel, the charismatic leader of the Protectors of Kronos, was arrested today on charges of tax evasion.

titulo: POK LEADER ARRESTE
oracion:
Michale Kraft, Karel's lawyer, released a statement asserting that the charges leveled against his client were "false" and that he hoped his client "would be released [from police custody] by week's end."

Police spokesman Adrien Carman responded the statement by Kraft, stating, "I think Mr. Kraft has underestimated the seriousness of his client's situation.

titulo: POK LEADER ARRESTE
oracion: We have been following his group closely for some time."

titulo: POK LEADER ARRESTE
oracion: Just last month, Karel's group was responsible for the trespassing incident that blocked entrance to the GAStech - Kronos headquarters.

titulo: POK LEADER ARRESTE
oracion: GAStech President and CEO Sten Sanjorge, Jr. condemned the POK as terrorists.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: Protesters aligned with the Protectors of Kronos (POK) activist group surrounded government buildings chanting and carry images of their so-called martyrs.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: Kronos government security forces in concert with Abila police suppressed the protest with an impressive show of force.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: Dressed in black the authorities donning helmets and gasmasks and brandishing riot shields, fired tear gas canisters as the protesters refused to disperse after several warnings.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: The group gathered proved reluctant to disperse even after the tear gas and the authorities pressed into the group protecting themselves with their shields and freely swinging their batons.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: In the face of overwhelming force, most of the protesters fled; however, a hard core group stood their ground suffering the consequences.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: The remaining protesters were surrounded by the riot police and after repeated baton blows many were dragged away under arrest.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: When the smoke cleared amongst the discarded and trampled banners and signs, blood was clearly visible on the plaza.

titulo: THREATS ISSUED BY PO
oracion: Letters purported to be from the Protectors of Kronos (POK) have been received by Vincent Kapelou, Minister of Health and nephew of President Kapelou.

titulo: THREATS ISSUED BY PO
oracion: The threatening letters appear to be the empty threats of an attention-seeking organization and nothing more.

titulo: THREATS ISSUED BY PO
oracion: Mr. Kapelou said, "Chances are this is nothing, but we're not going to take any chances."

titulo: THREATS ISSUED BY PO
oracion: Nonetheless he has doubled the size of his personal security force in response to the letters.

titulo: THREATS ISSUED BY PO
oracion: These sorts of threats only reinforce the fact that the POK are a "public threat" to quote President Kapelou.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL ISSUES STATEMENT ON ELODI
oracion: The international healthy water awareness group Wellness for All (WFA) have performed testing on the local water in Elodis finding high level of hazardous materials in residential water wells.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL ISSUES STATEMENT ON ELODI
oracion: In a statement released by WFA, the group directs blame to the Government of Kronos and GAStech International, a natural gas company from Tethys.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL ISSUES STATEMENT ON ELODI
oracion: In addition to directing blame WFA also demands that the two clean up the contamination, which includes high levels of benzene, toluene and xylene arsenic, barium, chromium, lead and selenium.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL ISSUES STATEMENT ON ELODI
oracion: By bringing attention to the contamination in and around Elodis, WFA expects the international community will pressure the Government of Kronos into action.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL ISSUES STATEMENT ON ELODI
oracion: Additionally, WFA has been working with the activist group Protectors of Kronos to lobby the government to apply pressure.

titulo: MEETING SET FOR TOMORROW MORNIN
oracion: With a meeting set tomorrow at 8 AM, the recent Initial Public Offering, and CEO Sten Sanjorge, Jr. in town reporters will be descending on the GAStech - Kronos headquarters in droves with plenty of questions.

titulo: MEETING SET FOR TOMORROW MORNIN
oracion: The Abila Post will be sending Haneson Ngohebo, writer of the On the Scene Blog, to live blog the event with the hopes of getting Sanjorge, Jr. and his GAStech - Kronos leadership group to comment on the IPO, their recent wind falls, and GAStech's plans for Kronos.
organizaciones: The Abila Post,the On the Scene Blog,GAStech - Kronos,GAStech,Kronos

titulo: GOVERNMENT CITES 'MINOR' CONTAMINATION NEAR ELODI
oracion: After continued complaints and appeals from the people of Elodis government officials acknowledge minor contamination in and around the rural township in a report on their investigation into the townspeople's health issues.

titulo: GOVERNMENT CITES 'MINOR' CONTAMINATION NEAR ELODI
oracion: However, the government report stops short of blaming GAStech International and its Tiskele Bend site 20 km upstream as the people of Elodis assert.

titulo: GOVERNMENT CITES 'MINOR' CONTAMINATION NEAR ELODI
oracion: The government report cites no root cause or causes can be determined at this time with more research and investigations needed.

titulo: GOVERNMENT CITES 'MINOR' CONTAMINATION NEAR ELODI
oracion: Indeed, "pointing a finger of blame at this time would be hasty and most likely detrimental to the investigation."

titulo: GOVERNMENT CITES 'MINOR' CONTAMINATION NEAR ELODI
oracion:
Though the report admits some contamination it goes on the qualify the level stating, "The minor level of contamination is well within international health standards agreed upon by the Government of Kronos and GAStech International as negotiated in the Tiskele Bend site contract."

The Government of Kronos continues to offer well testing for concerned residents of Elodis as well as plans to further investigate the root causes of the illnesses in and around the township.
organizaciones: the Government of Kronos,GAStech International,The Government of Kronos

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 1020 UPDATE -

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: People streamed out of the GAStech - Kronos headquarters about 5 minutes ago.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: There seemed to be much confusion and given the large corporate gathering today, this writer has doubts that it was a fire drill.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Perhaps an actual fire or a bomb threat could have caused the evacuation.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASE
oracion: For roughly 6 hours GAStech - Kronos employee Edvard Vann was interrogated by Kronos Police and Government officials before being released at 17:00 this evening.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASE
oracion: The apparent confusion stems from the similarity between his name and that of a Protector of Kronos member.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASE
oracion: Vann, a security guard for GAStech, was furious, stating, "I have nothing to do whatsoever with any members of the terrorist group POK.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASE
oracion: I know no one from Elodis.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASE
oracion: I was born here in Abila and I support my government and my president.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASE
oracion: Being accused and being interrogated for 6 hours as a terrorist POK member is one of the worst days of my life.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASE
oracion: Just because a person has the same name as a criminal does not make him a criminal."

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASE
oracion: Though he was instructed not to communicate with the press Vann was adamant to stress his innocence.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASE
oracion: With some 14 GAStech employees still unaccounted for, one cannot blame the police or the government for not leaving any stone unturned.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 1853 UPDATE - Speculation that the 2:00 PM arrival of Kronos Government official was in fact the arrival of a senior security executive and other officials from GAStech's Tethys office including President and CEO Sten Sanjorge, Jr.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: This speculation is based on information concerning the arrival, refueling and immediate departure of Sanjorge Jr.'s private jet from the Tethys airport.

titulo: PRESIDENT KAPELOU II ELECTED BY RECORD MARGI
oracion: President Dorel Kapelou II has won re-election with the largest margin ever in a Kronesian election.

titulo: PRESIDENT KAPELOU II ELECTED BY RECORD MARGI
oracion:
The people of Kronos have stood together and announced a bright new day with a resounding vote of confidence for the President.

President Kapelou II of the Democratic Party of Kronos captured 98.7% of the vote with Ren Touvi of the Organization of Business and Unions Party a distant second with a mere 1.0% of the vote.
organizaciones: the Democratic Party of Kronos,the Organization of Business and Unions Party

titulo: PRESIDENT KAPELOU II ELECTED BY RECORD MARGI
oracion: With all the votes counted the President's Democratic Party of Kronos now holds 85 seats in the General Assembly, 13 for the Organization of Business and Unions Party, and 2 for the Party of Kronos Industrialists.
organizaciones: Democratic Party of Kronos,the General Assembly,the Organization of Business and Unions Party,the Party of Kronos Industrialists

titulo: PRESIDENT KAPELOU II ELECTED BY RECORD MARGI
oracion: From every corner of Kronos could be heard a chorus of Kronos, Be Ever True to Thee.

titulo: DRUG RELATED ARRESTS ON THE RIS
oracion: An alarming new trend is sweeping Abila.

titulo: DRUG RELATED ARRESTS ON THE RIS
oracion: Police point out a dramatic increase in drug related arrests that may be linked to violent activist groups.

titulo: DRUG RELATED ARRESTS ON THE RIS
oracion: The port of Abila is known to be a transshipment point for drugs coming from the Middle East and Africa going to Europe namely heroin and hashish.

titulo: DRUG RELATED ARRESTS ON THE RIS
oracion: However, drug related arrests had remained flat over the past decade until the recent increase.

titulo: DRUG RELATED ARRESTS ON THE RIS
oracion: The concerns over the increase of drug related arrests are two-fold: first, violent activist groups such as the Protectors of Kronos could be using drug sales as a means to fund their activities; and second, with more drugs appearing on the shore, the people of Kronos will suffer increased drug related issues, namely addiction and violence.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 1100 UPDATE -

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Still no indication from the AFD about what if anything has happened; however, there are reports that the GAStech - Kronos employees gathered outside the building heard the fire alarm.

titulo: SPONTANEOUS PROTESTS ERUPT AROUND ABIL
oracion:
Protests erupted around the Kronos government buildings, downtown, and elsewhere around Abila eventually escalating into riots and violence. 

The activists are protesting the death yesterday of Elian Karel, a Protector of Kronos (POK) activist who died in jail after being arrested for tax evasion.

titulo: SPONTANEOUS PROTESTS ERUPT AROUND ABIL
oracion: However, the protests have turned violent with smashed windows and vandalized shops.

titulo: SPONTANEOUS PROTESTS ERUPT AROUND ABIL
oracion: Countless shop windows smashed in and around Siopa, the downtown shopping area.

titulo: SPONTANEOUS PROTESTS ERUPT AROUND ABIL
oracion: A general sense of chaos broke out with chanting protesters, fires, and fleeing citizens.

titulo: SPONTANEOUS PROTESTS ERUPT AROUND ABIL
oracion: A unifying theme of the protesters was the chanted slogans including "Justice for Elian" in reference to previously mentioned activist Elian Karel and "Remember Juliana", a young girl from Elodis who died in 1998 allegedly from the effects of water contamination.

titulo: SPONTANEOUS PROTESTS ERUPT AROUND ABIL
oracion: Several buildings were defaced with the above mentioned slogans as well.

titulo: SPONTANEOUS PROTESTS ERUPT AROUND ABIL
oracion: The Kronos government issued a statement, "This sort of violence will not be condoned.

titulo: SPONTANEOUS PROTESTS ERUPT AROUND ABIL
oracion: Destruction and violence is no way to achieve peace and change - these things are in opposition to each other.

titulo: SPONTANEOUS PROTESTS ERUPT AROUND ABIL
oracion: The Protectors of Kronos must resume peaceful means; all other approaches are unjustifiable."

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 934 UPDATE - Abila Police indicated that they are working with law enforcement and government officials from Tethys.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: The number of the missing has been revised from fourteen to ten.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: The names of the missing - and presumably kidnapped - have yet to be released.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Police stated that given the evolving nature of the incident announcing the names of the missing employees would simply add to the confusion, speculation, and potentially hinder the ongoing investigation.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: A GAStech International news conference has been announced for 10:00 this morning Kronos time.

titulo: ANNIVERSARY OF PROTEST
oracion: Last year spontaneous protests and riots broke out around Abila in response to the death of Elian Karel, a Protectors of Kronos (POK) activist.

titulo: ANNIVERSARY OF PROTEST
oracion: Officials fear a repeat of last year's violent activities around the city on the upcoming anniversary of Karel's death on June 19.

titulo: ANNIVERSARY OF PROTEST
oracion: Government officials issued a brief statement assuring the people of Abila that their "safety is of the utmost importance.

titulo: ANNIVERSARY OF PROTEST
oracion: Go about your business as usual.

titulo: ANNIVERSARY OF PROTEST
oracion: Groups like the Protectors of Kronos operate by fear, attempting to change lives and government through fear.

titulo: ANNIVERSARY OF PROTEST
oracion:
Your government will not back down to fear-mongering."

The brief government statement ended there with a promise not to back down to protesters, if there are indeed protests.

titulo: ANNIVERSARY OF PROTEST
oracion: Hagar Awelon, a shop-owner in Siopa district of Abila heavily impacted by last year's events, responded to the government statement: "They [Government of Kronos] must do more than they did last year.

titulo: ANNIVERSARY OF PROTEST
oracion: My windows were smashed, my goods destroyed or stolen, and my son was attacked when he defended the store.

titulo: ANNIVERSARY OF PROTEST
oracion: They must do more."

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 1330 UPDATE -

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: At 1315 we placed a call to GAStech headquarters.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: A hesitant administrative assistant to Orhan Strum, Chief Operating Officer of GAStech claimed Mr. Strum was unavailable.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Linda Lagos the assistant to Mr. Strum declined to answer any further questions about the incident, whether or not there was a fire, a false alarm, a bomb threat, or whether or not anyone is missing.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Uneasy throughout the call, Ms. Lagos repeated that Orhan Strum was unavailable at this time, said good bye and hung up.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Additional calls were placed with no answer on the GAStech end of the line.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 1235 UPDATE -

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Rumors abound in regards to the potentially missing GAStech executives.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Some suggest that the newly vested executive group skipped the government reception to avoid the press and left to an unknown resort location to celebrate their recent windfall.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: However, this rumor does not explain the police presence nor does it explain the fire department's search of GAStech headquarters.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: Abila Airport fueler Ravi Danisliau confirmed that two private jets took off today after being fueled.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: According to Danisliau, the seven or eight passengers of the first plane were "business types" and appeared to be in a hurry.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: It was not exactly clear where they were headed.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: The plane took off around 12:30 local Kronos time.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: The second plane also carried seven or eight "business types", but seemed "much more relaxed than the first group of passengers".

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: Danisliau said the second group of passengers "seemed to be celebrating something."

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: The second plane departed around 14:30 around two hours after the first plane.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: Danisliau confirmed that the second plane's destination was Rome, Italy.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: Between the two private jets that departed the Abila Airport fourteen to sixteen people could have been passengers.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: This could easily account for the leadership of GAStech - Kronos.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: When asked whether or not the two planes had anything to do with GAStech International Danisliau replied, "I don't ask a lot questions.

titulo: ABILA AIRPORT CONFIRMS TWO PRIVATE JETS LEFT TODA
oracion: I just fuel the planes."

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: The Kronos Government has labeled the Protectors of Kronos (POK) as a threat to the public.
organizaciones: The Kronos Government,the Protectors of Kronos,POK

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: In a statement by government spokesman Rufus Drymiau the POK are described as "justifiably a public threat due to violent demonstrations, opportunistic vandalism, and clashes with the police."

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: A shop owner in the Siopa district, who declined to be named, responded to the government labeling the POK a public threat: "I agree they are a public threat.

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: Every time they come around they bring their signs and then they smash windows.

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: We try to fight, but there are too many and they steal our things.

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: My business suffers because of the Protectors."

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: Officer Emilio Haber, who patrols the Siopa district, said of the POK, "They smash the windows.

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: They throw the rocks.

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: They chant for change and paint things on buildings.

titulo: GOVERNMENT LABELS POK 'PUBLIC THREAT'
oracion: They make themselves look stupid and then we arrest them and put them in jail where they belong."

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: 1520 UPDATE -

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: A report from the Abila Airport indicates that a private plane departed with eight people around 2:30 PM.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: The chartered jet was reportedly headed towards Rome, Italy.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: This report appears to confirm earlier rumors that members of the GAStech leadership simply avoided reporters and the Government reception.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: GAStech employees have begun to exit the building.

titulo: ON THE SCENE BLO
oracion: Hopefully they will shed light on today's events.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSIN
oracion: LOCATION: ABILA, Kronos

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSIN
oracion: Miriam Avila, an administrative assistant at GAStech International, has confirmed that members of the GAStech leadership are in fact missing.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSIN
oracion: The group was expected to arrive at the Government reception following this morning's meeting at GAStech - Kronos headquarters, but never showed up.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSIN
oracion: Ms. Avila denied that any GAStech employee has been abducted.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSIN
oracion: She also denied that they had simply skipped town with their newfound riches.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSIN
oracion: As The World reported on 16 December 2013, GAStech International's recent initial public offering (IPO) netted Sten Sanjorge, Jr. an eye-popping $1.96 billion for his controlling share of the international gas drilling and exploration company.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSIN
oracion: The GAStech - Kronos leadership was also handsomely rewarded.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSIN
oracion: The IPO filings show that the executive group earned a collective $327.25 million from the newly vested shares including $96.25 million each for CFO Ingrid Barranco, CIO Ada Campo-Corrente, and COO Orhan Strum.

oracion: In another unconscionable move against the citizens of Kronos, earlier today police arrested POK leader Elian Karel on spurious tax evasion charges.

titulo: POK LEADER KAREL ARRESTE
oracion: He was led - manacled - from a meeting of the Protectors of Kronos in Elodis, a rural township west of Abila.

titulo: POK LEADER KAREL ARRESTE
oracion: Demonstrating his trademark humor, Karel lifted his wrists and joked to his supporters as he is led away, "I guess I shouldn't have sent the President those cases of bottled water for his birthday."

oracion: Karel is the leader of the Protectors of Kronos, an alliance of Kronos citizens from Elodis that has demanded the government clean up the contaminated water caused by gas drilling in their community.

titulo: POK LEADER KAREL ARRESTE
oracion: "We didn't ask for GAStech to come to our community," Karel spoke at a rally a few months ago.

titulo: POK LEADER KAREL ARRESTE
oracion: "We didn't ask for our water to become undrinkable, for our children to become sick.

titulo: POK LEADER KAREL ARRESTE
oracion: Neither Elodis nor the people of Kronos have received any benefit from the extraordinarily large amount of money that GAStech clears every year.

titulo: POK LEADER KAREL ARRESTE
oracion:
I ask:  Where is the money going?"
The police representative assured supporters who massed outside the police station that Karel would be treated humanely, but declined to answer questions or allow visitors to see Karel.
"He's a determined man," Karel's attorney Michale Kraft told me over the phone.

titulo: POK LEADER KAREL ARRESTE
oracion: "He'll fight these false charges and be out in a few days.

titulo: POK LEADER KAREL ARRESTE
oracion:

Kraft plans to meet with Karel Saturday morning.

titulo: POK LEADER KAREL ARRESTE
oracion: Calls to the President and Minister of Justice offices were not immediately returned.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: This article is the second installment of a three-part series addressing the growing problem of one community's anguish, government malfeasance, and the alarming influence of multinational corporations on the country of Kronos.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: I caught up with Henk Bodrogi in town making purchases at Ferro Hardware store to repair a broken tractor.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: Bodrogi has farmed soybeans his entire life, as did his father and their fathers.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: I asked him about his life on the farm.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "We've worked the land for a long time - maybe 200 years, maybe a bit more," Henk Bodrogi told me as he picked over a container of bolts, searching for the right size.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "Over the years we've added a few hectares here and there.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion:
It keeps us busy."
Busy is an understatement, as I found when I prodded the wiry farmer to tell me more.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "I usually head to the fields before sun up," Mr. Henk Bodrogi tells me.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "My wife gets the kids up and heading to school, then she'll make a little something for us to eat for lunch and work alongside me until dinner.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: When the children get home from school they do their chores, and we're all back at the house most times by dark."

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "We do this most days," he adds, "except for worship days."

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: Bodrogi identifies the appropriate bolt and chats with the cashier about kids and school as he completes his purchase.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "We all know one another here," Bodrogi explains as we leave.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "Most families have lived here for generations.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: The first new people that came to town were with that gas company that built a few years back."

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: I ask Bodrogi if business has been good.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "We were doing pretty good until recently.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: Profits were good and we add acreage, or upgrade equipment.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion:
Then we started having all this trouble with the crops."
In what way, I asked.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "The crops aren't producing like they have in the past.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: It took a while to figure out, then one of the city officers figured out to call in a water specialist.  When they tested it they said the water was contaminated."

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: Bodrodgi sighed, and with a beleaguered look in his eye he thanked me for my interest and told me he had to head back home.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: The tractor had to be fixed before they could work the next day.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: I thanked him and watched him climb into his truck and head out of town.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: The water specialist turned out to be the international agency "Wellness For All", an international agency with a mission to bring healthy water to communities distressed by natural disasters, draught and - coincidentally - oil and gas development.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: I caught up with a representative from Wellness for All the next day.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: Joclyn Reynolds is project coordinator for "Wellness for All".

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: She spoke to me over a satellite call from her field office in Southeast Asia where she was setting up relief efforts following an earthquake.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: Ms. Reynolds agreed to speak to me for a few minutes between meetings about their work in Elodis.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "We were contacted by a city official about a problem they were having with their local water.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: In the last few years agriculture had foundered, and the incidence of certain illnesses and birth defects had risen.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: The Elodis drinking water comes from the Tiskele River, as does all the water for farming, so we looked for a source upstream.  We found sources of production waste disposal at the GAStech operation upstream.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion:
Tests showed high levels of benzene, toluene, xylene arsenic, lead and selenium, among other toxins. "
"Can these substances occur naturally?" I asked her.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "Not in these amounts, and not this suddenly.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: Groundwater contamination is usually the result of human activity.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: The GAStech pipes are releasing contaminants into a pond.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion:
The toxins are forming a subsurface plume that seeps into the Tiskele River from which the residents of Elodis draw their drinking water and irrigation for the crops."
"Did you talk to GAStech about this?"

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "Oh yes," she replied.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "At first we believed we were gaining traction.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: We met several times with GAStech representatives, including one of the senior executives, Hank Fluss.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: He personally assured us GAStech would act responsibly to provide material and financial assistance toward cleanup efforts.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: After a time, though, it became clear that while Mr. Fluss was earnest it was Sanjorge who makes the decisions.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: It is apparent that he [Sanjorge] has no interest in the wellbeing of the residents of Elodis, or the environment."

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: Sten Sanjorge, Jr., who had inherited his share in the company from his father in 1990, had developed a reputation for cutthroat business practices.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: "When we didn't make headway with GAStech," Reynolds continued, "the community leaders decided to approach the government of Kronos for assistance.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: Per our policy -and with permission from the Elodis leaders - we published the test results in an official public document.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion: The Elodis leaders then approached the government officials as citizens of a Kronesian community armed with the scientific analysis.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  HELP FROM AN UNEXPECTED SOURCE Part Tw
oracion:
Our agency assured them we would again be available to help in any way when those agreements were finalized."
At this point Ms Reynolds was called away from the phone, so I returned to my editor friend, Pondo Reese to tell finish the story.
Part Three will be published May 15, 1998

titulo: POK REMEMBERS MARTYRED LEADE

"

oracion: Among the demonstrators was Mestache Vardshvna, 23, from the west coast of Kronos.

titulo: PROTESTS SWELL IN ABILA IN RESPONSE TO CALLS TO ACTIO
oracion: "We're trying to get the attention of our government," he told the Homeland Illumination.

titulo: PROTESTS SWELL IN ABILA IN RESPONSE TO CALLS TO ACTIO
oracion:
"This is important, so I took time off from work to be a part of this important event."

He was one of many who wielded their power of free speech to voice their concern with the current lack of government transparency with public monies.

titulo: PROTESTS SWELL IN ABILA IN RESPONSE TO CALLS TO ACTIO
oracion: "They need to be aware that we know what they're doing," added Vardshvna.

titulo: PROTESTS SWELL IN ABILA IN RESPONSE TO CALLS TO ACTIO
oracion: "You can't just steal our money and think you can get away with it."

titulo: PROTESTS SWELL IN ABILA IN RESPONSE TO CALLS TO ACTIO
oracion: Posters with colorful images of Elian Karel and Juliana Vann were reminders of the heavy toll already paid by leaders and innocents.

titulo: PROTESTS SWELL IN ABILA IN RESPONSE TO CALLS TO ACTIO
oracion: Karel was the prior leader of the Protectors of Kronos before his premature death in 2009.

titulo: PROTESTS SWELL IN ABILA IN RESPONSE TO CALLS TO ACTIO
oracion: His death, thought to be a murder by many, prompted annul rallies to bring the message of the Protectors of Kronos to the public.

titulo: PROTESTS SWELL IN ABILA IN RESPONSE TO CALLS TO ACTIO
oracion: Juliana Vann died in 1998 of cancer caused by environmental toxins in her drinking water.

titulo: PROTESTS SWELL IN ABILA IN RESPONSE TO CALLS TO ACTIO
oracion: She had just turned ten years old.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: Two years ago yesterday Elian Karel died at age 28 in an Abila jail cell, purportedly of cardiac arrest.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: He had been arrested three months prior for spurious charges of tax evasion and left to linger in a jail cell without further legal action.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: His attorney, Michale Kraft made several appearances in court demanding that the government outline their specific charges, and release Karel.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: Kraft had reached an agreement with the government that charges would be reduced and the Karel be released pending a trial, but Karel died two days before he was to go free.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: Questions linger, however, about the manner of Karel's death.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: Requests for information were met with assurances that the police -whose custody Karel was in at the time of his death - would do everything possible to perform an exhaustive investigation.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: This "thorough investigation" lasted all of two weeks, including the time it took the Abila City Coroner to lose the original autopsy files.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion:
After Karel's body was cremated and sent to his family in Elodis, the Abila Chief of Police closed the case and has declined to answer questions about Karel's death stating that "we are satisfied the death was of natural causes and will no longer be entertaining inquiries."
As reported at the time of Karel's death, several people close to the investigation reported that Karel's body showed signs of blunt force trauma, abrasions and lacerations which were not consistent with the cause of death reported by the police.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: These confidential sources have since moved from the area and have been unavailable for contact.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: Police have denied anything unusual happened in Karel's death and city officials claim the accusations of murder and wrongful death are asserted by POK rabble-rousers attempting to incite instability and violence.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: Yesterday on the morning of June 19th, a small group of POK supporters gathered in front of the Abila Police Station, holding photographs of Elian, and of another young martyr, Juliana Vann, the ten-year old girl who died in 1998 from cancer caused by benzene toxins in her drinking water.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: "Both of them died because of government lies and corruption," one man told me who asked that his name be withheld because of concerns of police retaliation.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: "Juliana died because Kronos allowed GAStech to poison our water, and Elian died because he tried to bring Juliana justice.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion:
When will it end?"
Another, larger crowd had gathered the day before in a nearby city park to bring public awareness about these same issues.

titulo: A LOOK BACK AT A LIFE CUT TRAGICAL SHORT: ELIAN KARE
oracion: Amid the speeches and music, I heard the same message from the year before:  "Remember Juliana! Remember Elian!"

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: Thousands of protesters carrying banners reading "Remember Juliana!" and chanting "We want truth!" rallied in front of the Kronos government offices Saturday morning.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: Protesters were demanding an accounting of the government revenues from then President Araullo's tax incentives that were signed into law in 1993.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: Ten-year old Juliana Vann died in 1998 from an illness caused by contaminated water from GAStech drilling operations.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: She has become the heart-rending icon of a movement that has gained support from one end of Kronos to the other.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: "We were promised better jobs, new roads, better healthcare and a better standard of living," said one 20-year old protestor who declined to have her name used.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: "All I see are bigger mansions for the ministers and a hospital that costs more to fix than it can make.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion:
We won't accept that!"
The protestor was referring to Abila General Hospital built in 1997 ostensibly with money from the increased revenue from the foreign gas operations here on Kronos.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: The non-profit hospital has had difficulty maintaining its infrastructure, despite the extensive restoration performed sevearl years ago to replace the electrical and plumbing systems.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: "The contracts were all given to family and cronies of the ministers," accuses 26-year old Jon L., who traveled six hours to attend yesterday's rally.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: "What we need is transparency in our government.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: We need to know what happens to all the money coming in from these foreign companies.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: Protest leader Elian Karel addressed the demonstrators at Abila City park.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: Karel took over POK leadership from Henk Bodrogi, whose ill health forced him down from the position.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: Karel spoke eloquently about the beginnings of the POK campaign as a grassroots effort for clean water, to the dynamic movement it has become demanding improved government transparency and accountability.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: "We aren't asking for anything unreasonable," Karel speaks passionately to his ardent listeners.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: "All we want is to know how our taxes are being used.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: We know these corporations are generating records profits at the expense of Kronos, but we see none of the promised improvements.

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: All we want is accountability for those who died because of greed, corruption and disregard of those who they should be protecting."

titulo: POK RALLY DRAWS THOUSANDS OF SUPPORTER
oracion: Calls to the President's office were not immediately returned.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: Earlier this year a series Homeland Illumination published a series of articles about groundwater contamination in Elodis, and how the locals are demanding a government response for what is essentially Government of Kronos-sponsored pollution and poisoning of citizens.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: This article is an update.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: ELODIS, Kronos -

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: Ten-year old Juliana Vann died yesterday afternoon, surrounded by her family and friends.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: The cause of death was leukemia due to benzene poisoning.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: Juliana had been sick for over a year.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: Initially her family didn't realize that benzene poisoning was the cause of Juliana's problems.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: After visits to many hospitals, a doctor associated with the international assistance organization Wellness For All recommended Juliana be tests for benzene poisoning.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: At that point, however, the little girl's system was too damaged to recover.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: The residents of Elodis have been pleading with the government of Kronos to take action against the pollution caused by the GAStech gas drilling operation just 20 km upstream from Elodis.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: Juliana's death is but one of several deaths this rural township has suffered because of toxic waste being dumped into the Tiskele River by Tethys corporation GAStech.

titulo: TEN-YEAR OLD ELODIS GIRL DIES OF POISONIN
oracion: Private funeral services will be held on August 21 in the family home.

ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: This article is the last installment of a three-part series addressing the growing problem of one community's anguish, government malfeasance, and the alarming influence of multinational corporations on the country of Kronos.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: Pondo Reese, editor of the Elodis Weekly Journal, stands at his window, looking out toward the sun setting on the Tiskele River.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: I've asked him to tell me about the involvement of the government of Kronos in the deeply troubling account of a community's struggle for protection from those who should help them the most: their elected officials, against those who would poison their children and the country's food.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: "It took a long time for anyone to respond," Reese tells me of their struggle.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: "Henk Bodrogi - the man you met - didn't give up.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion:
He called every department that could possibly be associated with our problem:  interior, justice, foreign affairs, health.    Henk and a few other residents made several trips to Abila trying to get someone to listen.  Finally, a sympathetic person from the Ministry of Health answered the door, so that's where we started."
Reese then describes months of meetings at which the government officials demanded documents proving their case:  health and crop yield statistics, the scientific test results from Wellness For All, and medical records.
organizaciones: the Ministry of Health,Wellness For All

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: "It's been frustrating.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: We bring the documents they want, and then they want to confirm the results, or tell us to provide additional information or have closed door meetings.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion:
We're currently in the process of negotiating a date for a hearing at the Ministry of Health to present our petition for assistance."
Has it been worth it?

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: "You tell me," Reese nods out his window.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: I look over his shoulder to see a group of children kicking a soccer ball in the dust.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS: WILL THE GOVERNMENT RESPOND IN TIME? Part Thre
oracion: "What choice do we have?"

ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: This article is the first installment of a three-part series addressing the growing problem of one community's anguish, government malfeasance, and the alarming influence of multinational corporations on the country of Kronos.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: ELODIS, Kronos -

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: Nestled in the bend of the Tiskele River, the sun rises over the farming town of Elodis,  chasing away the shadows cloaking nearby Mt. Bouro.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: Today, as they have every day for over 250 years, residents will rise to tend the rich floodplain land that provides nourishment for the People of Kronos.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: Two weeks prior I received an email from an old friend, Pondo Reese, now the editor of the Elodis Weekly Journal, an agriculture paper serving the community around Tiskele Bend.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: In his email he described a once bountiful region now distressed by contamination, struggling to find solutions to a worsening problem.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: I decided to investigate.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: "We didn't make the connection at first," Reese told me when I met with him at his office.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: "The gas company had been built a few years back in '94, and our problems didn't start right away.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: After a couple of harvests, we saw a decline in the production.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: We thought perhaps it was just a hiccup, and things would get better.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion:
Then when the kids started getting sick we took a harder look at what could have changed."
The change turned out to be GAStech International, an international corporation run by Sten Sanjorge Jr, a business tycoon out of Tethys.
Established in 1961, the GAStech corporation began as a family-owned business providing local trucking services in Tethys.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: The two founders - Sten Sanjorge Sr and Hank Fluss - found wildcat drilling to be more lucrative, and thus began a series of environmental disasters and financial scandals that eventually ran Sanjorge Sr into an early grave and drove Fluss into a marginal role in his own company.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: With the death of Sanjorge Sr, the son took the helm of GAStech firmly in his grasp and broadened its influence further afield, eventually landing at the doorstep of the small peaceful township of Elodis.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: With a population of 6500, most residents of Elodis live in one- and two-story houses on small farms.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: A smaller number of families live in the township along a main street with two markets, two hardware stores, one gas station and a café where you can buy lunch, pick up your mail and purchase a litre of milk to bring home.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: Families have lived in Elodis for generations.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: "We've made a good living for a long time," Reese tells me.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: "The population has been steadily increasing.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: Crop production has been good.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: For the most part, kids haven't left for the city as they have in a lot of other rural places.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: We have a lot of land that could yet be developed.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: There was a future for them here."

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: I asked Reese to help me meet the people whose lives have been impacted by GAStech's operations.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: He introduced me to a farmer whose family had been here for several generations.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: I caught up with Henk Bodrogi in town making purchases at the Osvaldo hardware store to repair a broken tractor.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: Bodrogi has farmed soybeans his entire life, as did his father and their fathers.

titulo: ELODIS, KRONOS:  A TOWN IN NEED, Part On
oracion: I asked him about his life on the farm.

oracion: Part Two will be published April 25, 1998
