POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion: Government heavies obstructed the free speech - yet again - of members of the activist group Protectors of Kronos yesterday at a lawful demonstration at the Tiskele Bend fields.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion:
The five POK activists had gathered in front of the gates to GAStech gas drilling operations facility to bring public awareness about the polluted Tiskele River which has caused health problems to the residents of Elodis.
Bystanders report that the demonstration had begun peacefully with the five POK members walking back and forth across the road, chanting "Remember Juliana!" and "No more poison!"

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion: An eyewitness told the Homeland Illumination that when the gates opened to allow GAStech company vehicles to exit the facility the protesters moved aside.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion:
Witnesses agree that at the same time vehicles with the Government of Kronos seal drove to the gates, apparently planning to enter the facility. 
"It was all very civil up till then," Griffith Mabel, an Elodis resident who had come out to support the POK told the Homeland Illumination.   "The gates opened, the POK people moved and the trucks drove out.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion: That's when it got weird.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion: The trucks stopped in the middle of the road for no reason."

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion: Another eyewitness, Elodis farmer Charley Normand adds, "Yeah, the POK guys asked the drivers to move nicely, but the GAStech drivers ignored them.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion:
They had their windows down, so it wasn't like they couldn't hear them."
The occupants of the government vehicles exited and joined the altercation.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion: The sequence of events becomes confusing at this point.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion: Some witnesses state the GAStech drivers instigated arguments with the protestors, and others think the government officials began to strong arm the protesters from the road.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion: "Turns out the people in the government cars were police," Mabel tells the Homeland Illumination.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion:
"They wore uniforms and had badges."
Onlookers tell the Homeland Illumination that the three parties began yelling, and at some point the Kronos police - presumably from Abila-  arrested the five activists and transported them to an Elodis jail.

titulo: POK MEMBERS ARRESTE
oracion: Despite repeated requests for an interview, the Homeland Illumination has not been granted access to those arrested.

titulo: Kronos Benefits from Foreign Investmen
oracion: The hypocrisy of bringing in foreigners to tell us that opening our country to foreigners is bad for us is ludicrous and is obviously a sign of mental illness in those who oppose our modernization.

oracion: Minster Nespola has long been a strong advocate of the health and well-being of our citizens, and his support for this measure adds to a long list of the actions he has undertaken on our behalf.

oracion: It is with great sorrow that we announce the death of Minister of Health Cesare Nespola.

titulo: Minister of Health Dies Suddenl
oracion: Minister Nespola, 62, died peacefully in his sleep yesterday of a suspected heart attack.

titulo: Minister of Health Dies Suddenl
oracion: A tireless champion for the welfare of our people, Nespola was a physician who had been picked to lead the Ministry of Health in 1995 by former president Araullo.

titulo: Minister of Health Dies Suddenl
oracion: He was popular enough that President Kapelou retained him when he formed his cabinet in 2000.

titulo: Minister of Health Dies Suddenl
oracion: Shortly after hearing of Nespola's death, President Kapelou announced that his nephew Vincent Kapelou would serve as his administration's new Minister of Health.

titulo: Minister of Health Dies Suddenl
oracion: Vincent Kapelou, 28, has a Bachelor's of Science in chemistry and a Master's of Science in biochemistry from Tethys Central University.

oracion: The Protectors of Kronos (POK) are suspected of kidnapping up to fourteen GAStech employees from their headquarters building earlier today.

oracion: The POK has made no statements regarding the kidnapping.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Constructio
oracion: President Araullo announced today that his government is planning the construction of a new, modern Abila General Hospital.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Constructio
oracion: The old Abila General Hospital, built in 1930, has outdated health care facilities and has suffered numerous electrical fires in the past decade.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Constructio
oracion: Hospital Administrator Torsten Trucco lauded the government's action saying, "We've been trying to get funding to update our facilities for years, to no avail.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Constructio
oracion: We have been living on borrowed time for quite a while now with the old boiler.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Constructio
oracion:
It's been pure luck that the old girl hasn't failed on us completely."

The new Abila General will have 350 beds, a substantial upgrade from the mere 100 beds of the current antiquated facility.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Constructio
oracion: Additionally, it will have a full emergency services area, trauma and burn care units, a psychiatric care wing, and four ultra-modern surgical suites.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Constructio
oracion: In his announcement of the new construction, Araullo said, "Our strategy of courting foreign investment is paying great dividends.

titulo: Araullo Announces New Hospital Constructio
oracion: This new hospital is the first of many projects we plan to pursue to help upgrade our standard of living and modernize our lifestyle."

titulo: GAStech and Kronos Celebrate Partnershi

titulo: Grand Opening of the New GAStech Office
oracion: The gleaming steel and glass building provides ample office space for regional managers, geologists, engineers, and support staff, and sports state-of-the art conference facilities.

titulo: Grand Opening of the New GAStech Office
oracion: Minister Sarto, who attended the celebration, said, "This beautiful facility is a monument to Sanjorge's commitment to Kronos and should be seen by the citizens as a sign of a prosperous future for all."

titulo: POK Labeled a "Public Threat

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrest
oracion: Dozens of protesters attending a Protectors of Kronos (POK) rally in front of the GAStech regional headquarters in Abila were arrested for trespassing this morning.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrest
oracion: The POK rally was intended to draw attention to their claims of environmental damage being caused by the development of gas and oil fields around Kronos by foreign corporations like GAStech.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrest
oracion: About two hundred people gathered in front of the GAStech building chanting slogans and waving signs that held the visages of people who have allegedly died due to environmental contamination.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrest
oracion: Ten of the protestors chained themselves to the doors of the building in an attempt to prevent GAStech employees from going to work.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrest
oracion: Police spokesman Adrien Carman said, "We allowed the group some latitude with their rally, but when GAStech complained that the protestors were blocking entrance to their building, we had to take action.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrest
oracion:
The last thing we wanted to happen was for a GAStech employee to get hurt by the crowd just because he was trying to go to work."

The POK, once a small political activist group of citizens from the Elodis area, has been revitalization under the charismatic leadership of Elian Karel.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrest
oracion: Government spokesman Rufus Drymiau said of today's POK rally, "We have been concerned by a pattern of increasingly aggressive tactics by the Protectors of Kronos for some time now.

titulo: POK Protest at GAStech Headquarters Ends in Arrest

oracion: More than a dozen POK protesters were handcuffed and taken into custody by police Tuesday for blocking access to the Tiskele Bend fields.

titulo: Protestors Block Traffic to Tiskele Bend Field
oracion: Before police made the arrests shortly after 9 a.m., the protesters were told they were breaking the law for trespassing on government property, blocking access to government-owned land, and impeding lawful commercial traffic.

titulo: Protestors Block Traffic to Tiskele Bend Field
oracion: The protesters arrived at the entrance to the Tiskele Bend site about 5:30 a.m. and locked arms across the road for about three hours, despite being asked to leave by police.

titulo: Protestors Block Traffic to Tiskele Bend Field
oracion: As traffic on the road began to back up, several truck drivers began to leave their vehicles and congregate near the protesters.

titulo: Protestors Block Traffic to Tiskele Bend Field
oracion: Tempers began to flare as the blockade persisted into the second hour, and the drivers started shouting and cursing at the protesters to move out of the road.  Police officers quickly moved in and arrested the POK protesters before the situation could escalate to violence.

titulo: Protestors Block Traffic to Tiskele Bend Field
oracion: "We appreciate citizens voicing their opinion, but the middle of a busy road is not the right forum for a discussion of our national environmental policy.

titulo: Protestors Block Traffic to Tiskele Bend Field

oracion: A motion to increase taxes on oil and gas development by an additional 10% was defeated today in the General Assembly by a vote of 77 to 23.

titulo: Added Taxes on Oil, Gas Development Defeated in General Assembly
oracion: The proposed tax increase, championed by Minister of Health Cesare Nespola, was to provide specific funding for health care, clean water projects, and health education for rural areas.

titulo: Added Taxes on Oil, Gas Development Defeated in General Assembly
oracion: Minister Nespola said of the Assembly vote, "I'm disappointed by the vote, but the Assembly was concerned that the increase in tax would discourage foreign investment in our energy sector.

titulo: Added Taxes on Oil, Gas Development Defeated in General Assembly
oracion: This is a setback to my program to help our rural townships, but I am nothing if not persistent.

titulo: Added Taxes on Oil, Gas Development Defeated in General Assembly
oracion: My office will be sending a revised added tax measure to the Assembly later this year.

titulo: Added Taxes on Oil, Gas Development Defeated in General Assembly
oracion: Additionally, I will work with President Kapelou's office to restructure the allocation of funds from current gas and oil taxes to provide for rural health projects."

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates
oracion: Update, 11:45 AM:

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates
oracion: Fire department officials allow GAStech employees to re-enter the building.

oracion: Update, 6:10 PM:

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates
oracion: The GAStech executive jet reportedly arrived in Tethys a few hours ago bearing Sten Sanjorge Jr.  The jet was quickly refueled and then departed for Abila International Airport with six GAStech officials onboard.

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates
oracion: The GAStech executive jet arrived at the airport.

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates
oracion: The occupants were taken by limousine to the GAStech building.

titulo: Minister of Health Receives Threats from PO
oracion: Police sources have informed the Kronos Star that Vincent Kapelou, Minister of Health, has received several threatening letters purporting to come from the POK.

titulo: Minister of Health Receives Threats from PO
oracion: "I guess they're getting desperate for attention," Vincent Kapelou said in a phone interview.

titulo: Minister of Health Receives Threats from PO
oracion: "Chances are this is nothing, but we're not going to take any chances.

titulo: Minister of Health Receives Threats from PO
oracion:
I have doubled the size of my security force and sent my family away on an extended vacation."

Kapelou, 39, was appointed to the position of Minister of Health in 2001 after the death of Cesare Nespola.

titulo: Minister of Health Receives Threats from PO
oracion: Kapelou is the oldest son of President Kaeplou's brother, Andreas.

titulo: Government Announces Tax Incentives For Foreign Investmen
oracion: Today the Parliament voted 86 to 14 in favor of President Araullo's package of tax incentives designed to lure foreign investment to our fair country.

titulo: Government Announces Tax Incentives For Foreign Investmen
oracion: Tomas Sarto, Minister of the Interior, lauded the vote as "a landmark deal designed to better the lives of all Kronosians".

titulo: Government Announces Tax Incentives For Foreign Investmen
oracion: The tax incentives specifically target energy development companies, which the government hopes to lure to Kronos' rich, but yet undeveloped, gas fields.

titulo: Government Announces Tax Incentives For Foreign Investmen
oracion: Ministry of the Interior projections show that development of just the Tiskele Bend fields could bring in as many as 5,000 high paying jobs and yield billions of dollars of infrastructure development over the next 20 years.

titulo: Ministry of Health Investigates Contamination Complaint
oracion: Minister of Health Cesare Nespola announced today that his organization would be investigating claims of abnormal health issues in areas surrounding the Tiskele Bend drill site.

titulo: Ministry of Health Investigates Contamination Complaint
oracion: Minister Nespola said, "We have no reason to believe that the drilling at Tiskele Bend has resulted in any contamination of surface or well water in the region.

titulo: Ministry of Health Investigates Contamination Complaint
oracion: However, I believe it is important as Minister of Health to do due diligence and investigate the reports of sickness near the Elodis township.

titulo: Ministry of Health Investigates Contamination Complaint
oracion: Taking care of our people is my number one priority."

titulo: Ministry of Health Investigates Contamination Complaint
oracion: In related news, a press release from Nespola's office proclaimed that his office has granted a license to practice medicine to a Tethys oncologist, making him the first licensed oncologist in Kronos history.

titulo: Ministry of Health Investigates Contamination Complaint
oracion: Dr. Ronald Gerard will be a resident at the Abila General Hospital.

titulo: GAStech's Sanjorge Escapes Kidnapping at GAStech H
oracion: According to a press conference held at GAStech headquarters in Centrum, Tethys this morning, GAStech's President and CEO, Sten Sanjorge Jr. returned safely to Tethys after a reported kidnapping event his company's headquarters building in Abila yesterday.

titulo: GAStech's Sanjorge Escapes Kidnapping at GAStech H
oracion: Sanjorge, who had been attending a corporate meeting, was in transit from the GAStech building to the capitol when the kidnapping took place.

titulo: GAStech's Sanjorge Escapes Kidnapping at GAStech H
oracion: Sanjorge and the four executives from the local GAStech headquarters were to attend a reception being hosted by President Kapelou at the Capitol Building.

titulo: GAStech's Sanjorge Escapes Kidnapping at GAStech H
oracion: The reception was held to celebrate the 20th year of cooperation between the corporation and our country.

titulo: GAStech's Sanjorge Escapes Kidnapping at GAStech H
oracion: At the press conference, the GAStech spokesperson said, "Our hearts go out to the families of the kidnapped.

titulo: GAStech's Sanjorge Escapes Kidnapping at GAStech H
oracion: We are working for a speedy and safe resolution to this crisis."

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates

oracion: One GAStech employee, who declined to be identified, reports having seen several people dressed in black in the building before the fire alarm.

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates
oracion: These people were not GAStech employees are "were acting odd and lurking about".

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates

Unofficial reports from the police indicate that they believe the Protectors of Kronos (POK) are behind the kidnapping and that they requested government assistance with the investigation.

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates
oracion: We have received no information which could confirm the POK's role in this alleged kidnapping, but note that they have grown increasingly violent over the past 5 years.

titulo: Breaking: Emergency at GAStech Headquarters Building [Updates
oracion: Police have not commented on their activities.

titulo: Protest Turns Violent in Abil
oracion: A rally of hundreds of protestors allied with the "Protectors of Kronos" movement turned to violence today as angry activists vented their displeasure on the innocent citizens of Abila after hearing the news of POK leader Elian Karel's death.

titulo: Protest Turns Violent in Abil
oracion: Karel, who had been awaiting trial for tax evasion, was found dead in his jail cell yesterday morning.

titulo: Protest Turns Violent in Abil
oracion: The POK assembly began peacefully enough with the usual chanted slogans and waving of protest signs, but then one young rabble-rouser grabbed a bullhorn and began inciting the crowd to violence.

titulo: Protest Turns Violent in Abil
oracion: The crowd smashed windows and vandalized shops in the Siopa area, set fires in the streets, and clashed with police.

titulo: Protest Turns Violent in Abil
oracion: Additional police forces responded to contain the chaos and they were forced to use rubber bullets and tear gas in order to disperse the crowds.

titulo: Protest Turns Violent in Abil
oracion: President Kapelou's office released a statement about the rally, stating, "This sort of violence will not be condoned.

titulo: Protest Turns Violent in Abil
oracion: Destruction and violence is no way to achieve peace and change - these things are in opposition to each other.

titulo: Protest Turns Violent in Abil
oracion: The Protectors of Kronos must resume peaceful means; all other approaches are unjustifiable."

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Rio
oracion: POK members held a large demonstration in Abila yesterday.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Rio
oracion: Several dozen of their supporters held sit-ins in front of the capitol building and the presidential manor, while others took to the streets with their signs and chants.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Rio
oracion: Protestors handed out flyers to bystanders that alleged that our government is corrupt and "the rich get richer on the backs of the poor".

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Rio
oracion: Police called for the peaceful end to the sit-ins, but were answered with a barrage of rocks and bottles from the crowd.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Rio
oracion: The violence escalated into a full blown riot and police were forced to use tear gas, pepper spray, water cannons, and beanbags shot from shotguns to control the crowd.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Rio
oracion: By the time the crowds finally dispersed, several government buildings had been vandalized, two police vehicles were ablaze, and the streets were littered with trash and broken glass.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Rio
oracion: Several protestors and police were injured, including one heroic police officer who was stabbed by a crazed protestor.

titulo: POK Anniversary Rally Ends in Rio
oracion: The officer, whose name has been withheld for security reasons, is in critical condition at Abila General Hospital.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Agai
oracion: POK members held their annual demonstration in Abila yesterday.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Agai
oracion: A larger than usual crowd gathered in front of the Capitol building, waving signs holding pictures of Elian Karel and Juliana Vann, who were painted as POK "martyrs".

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Agai
oracion: The crowds chanted about government corruption and called for President Dorel Kapelou to step down.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Agai
oracion:
Several protestors carried signs calling for an end to the "exploitive Tethys corporate capitalism" and alleging, "GAStech poisoned our kids".  

Police and government security forces set up between the protestors and the Capitol building in a show of force, hoping to prevent the kind of chaos that occurred during last year's riot.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Agai
oracion: However, after several hours of chanting and speeches, tempers in the crowd flared and protestors rushed the police line.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Agai
oracion: The police forces were forced to use tear gas, pepper spray, water cannons, and rubber bullets to subdue the crowd and protect property.

titulo: Annual POK Rally Ends in Riot, Agai
oracion: In spite of their heroic efforts, the protestors managed to break some windows, damage several police vehicles, and injure three officers.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarter
oracion: A Protectors of Kronos demonstration was held in front of Abila police headquarters yesterday morning.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarter
oracion: The POK had gathered in memorialize their former leader, Elian Karel, who died of natural causes in jail last year.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarter
oracion:
POK supporters carried signs with pictures of Karel and Juliana Vann, chanted slogans, and lit candles. 

The peaceful demonstration turned violent when two POK members accosted a man who attempted to enter the building on business.  The POK members hit him with a bottle, which knocked him to the ground and gave him a bloody gash on his forehead.  Abila police attempted to gain control of the situation by using bullhorns to call for the peaceful dispersal of the crowd, but the crowd responded to their calls by hurling insults along with a few rocks at the officers.  Police used tear gas to end the gathering, but a handful of die-hard POK members urged the crowd into melee with the officers.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarter
oracion: Additional security forces had to be summoned to help contain the situation as the violence escalated.  When the tear gas finally cleared, six POK member were arrested on charges of assault on civil authorities and inciting a crowd to violence.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarter
oracion: Three police officers were treated at Abila General Hospital for wounds received in the fight.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarter
oracion: "We had been concerned that Silvia Marek's weak leadership is allowing the POK to be taken over by criminals and hooligans.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarter
oracion: Today's events show that our concerns were valid," said police spokesman Adrien Carman.

titulo: POK Protest at Abila Police Headquarter
oracion: Marek replaced Elian Karel as the popular figurehead of the POK movement last summer.

titulo: UPGRADES NEEDED FOR ABILA'S DEEP WATER POR
oracion: As part of the government brokered deal with GAStech International, Abila must make upgrades to their deep water port.

titulo: UPGRADES NEEDED FOR ABILA'S DEEP WATER POR
oracion: When gas production ramps up, the Port's traffic is expected to increase ten-fold.

titulo: UPGRADES NEEDED FOR ABILA'S DEEP WATER POR
oracion: The proposed upgrades include raising Abila's East Pier in phases, a massive $300 million project that will accommodate new, larger container ships.

titulo: UPGRADES NEEDED FOR ABILA'S DEEP WATER POR
oracion: Currently the East Pier is roughly 3 meters above sea level and must be raised to 8 meters.

titulo: UPGRADES NEEDED FOR ABILA'S DEEP WATER POR
oracion: Additionally, the Port will need to dredge the port killing two birds with one stone: increasing the depth of the port and providing fill to raise the East Pier.

titulo: UPGRADES NEEDED FOR ABILA'S DEEP WATER POR
oracion: Port of Abila's Director Claudio Morluniau applauded the deal saying that the additional port capacity will open doors for import and export trade.

titulo: UPGRADES NEEDED FOR ABILA'S DEEP WATER POR
oracion: "This deal and the port expansion is the introduction of Kronos to the world!"

titulo: PROMINENT BUSINESS, CIVIC LEADER DIES AT 6
oracion: After four years of diminishing health following a major heart attack, Sten Sanjorge, Sr. died early Friday morning.

titulo: PROMINENT BUSINESS, CIVIC LEADER DIES AT 6
oracion: Sanjorge, Sr., 65, of Centrum, Tethys was President Emeritus of GAStech International having founded the company in 1961.

titulo: PROMINENT BUSINESS, CIVIC LEADER DIES AT 6
oracion: In addition to his role at GAStech International was the chairman of the Centrum Chamber board of directors and member of the Centrum Children's Hospital Board of Trustees.
organizaciones: GAStech International,Centrum Chamber,the Centrum Children's Hospital Board of Trustees

titulo: PROMINENT BUSINESS, CIVIC LEADER DIES AT 6
oracion: "Sten has always been a champion for the children of Tethys," said Hospital President Willem Gracias.

titulo: PROMINENT BUSINESS, CIVIC LEADER DIES AT 6
oracion: "He was a true servant leader and endlessly worked to drive our institution forward.

titulo: PROMINENT BUSINESS, CIVIC LEADER DIES AT 6
oracion:
Sten will truly be missed and we ask that everyone keep the Sanjorge family in their thoughts and prayers."

Sanjorge, Sr. is survived by his wife Ingrid Sanjorge and his son Sten Sanjorge, Jr.

"A great light in this world has been extinguished, yet he still casts a shadow," said Sanjorge, Jr.

titulo: PROMINENT BUSINESS, CIVIC LEADER DIES AT 6
oracion: "I vow to lead our company forward with a renewed vision and dignity that will honor my father's life and work."

titulo: KRONOS GOVERNMENT PLANS TAX BREAKS TO ENCOURAGE FOREIGN INVESTMEN
oracion: The Government of Kronos is currently planning some of the world's most generous tax breaks for gas investments.

titulo: KRONOS GOVERNMENT PLANS TAX BREAKS TO ENCOURAGE FOREIGN INVESTMEN
oracion: This will help create "cheap energy" that can give the developing country a competitive advantage and a leg up in the government's push to modernize.

titulo: KRONOS GOVERNMENT PLANS TAX BREAKS TO ENCOURAGE FOREIGN INVESTMEN
oracion: As high-income countries from Europe and the United States race to take advantage of existing and potential gas deposits, Kronos is planning to provide incentives such as reducing corporate and individual tax, preferential tariffs, and derogations from regulations as well as cheap, but eager work force.

titulo: KRONOS GOVERNMENT PLANS TAX BREAKS TO ENCOURAGE FOREIGN INVESTMEN
oracion: The Government of Kronos is pitching the plan as a win-win situation given that the high-income countries will be struggling to discover and exploit ever-dwindling supplies of fossil-fuels and the developing Kronos needs income, infrastructure, and cheap energy.

titulo: KRONOS GOVERNMENT PLANS TAX BREAKS TO ENCOURAGE FOREIGN INVESTMEN
oracion: Look for energy companies to flock to Kronos.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: After a long day of conflicting and confusing information reports are still sketchy, but the story is beginning to come clear: a Kronos Government source has confirmed up to fourteen of GAStech International's employees may have been kidnapped at the company's headquarters in Abila.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: Much speculation remains regarding who was taken in the kidnapping.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: Speculation includes whether or not GAStech International President and CEO Sten Sanjorge Jr. was the target given that GAStech International has yet to make a statement to the press.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: Speculation about the motivation behind the kidnapping has also been rampant due to the recent GAStech IPO.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: At this time no one has claimed responsibility for the kidnapping.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: Edvard Vann, a GAStech - Kronos security guard who was interrogated and released after 6 hours, indicated the Protectors of Kronos were suspected as being the perpetrators behind today's events.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: A GAStech International senior security executive has been on site to support the investigation, aiding the Abila Police Department and Kronos Government officials.
organizaciones: GAStech International,the Abila Police Department,Kronos Government

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: January 20th was GAStech's annual corporate meeting.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: At some point while company officers were transitioning from the main office to a Kronos Government reception the abductions took place.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: Unconfirmed reports of a fire at the office may have served as a distraction for the kidnappers or at least contributed to the confusion during the event.

titulo: KIDNAPPING AT GASTECH KRONOS
oracion: Abila Fire Department trucks were dispatched to GAStech - Kronos headquarters around 10:00 this morning local Kronos time to respond to a fire alarm.

titulo: HANK FLUSS GASTECH COO DIES AT 7
oracion: Hank Fluss, COO of GAStech International, died of a heart attack at his desk in the company's downtown Centrum headquarters.

titulo: HANK FLUSS GASTECH COO DIES AT 7
oracion: Though Fluss was 73 years old, his death came as a shock.

titulo: HANK FLUSS GASTECH COO DIES AT 7
oracion: Hank Fluss spent 40 years with GAStech, befriending Sten Sanjorge, Sr. in 1963 when the two started out on their own.

titulo: HANK FLUSS GASTECH COO DIES AT 7
oracion: As wildcatters, they began drilling in areas not previously known to be gas fields.

titulo: HANK FLUSS GASTECH COO DIES AT 7
oracion: After many failed wells and on the brink of financial ruin, Fluss and Sanjorge, Sr. pressed on eventually finding one of the largest untapped gas fields in Tethys.

titulo: HANK FLUSS GASTECH COO DIES AT 7
oracion: As Chief Operating Officer, Fluss has overseen GAStech's expansion, truly making it an international company and growing it into a multi-billion dollar operation.

titulo: HANK FLUSS GASTECH COO DIES AT 7
oracion: Always a champion of environmental causes, Fluss had become increasingly disenchanted with the GAStech - Kronos operation straining his relationship with CEO Sten Sanjorge, Jr.

titulo: HANK FLUSS GASTECH COO DIES AT 7
oracion: Hank Fluss is survived by his wife of 54 years, Beatriz Fluss, his 5 children, and 12 grandchildren.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL (WFA) BLASTS GASTECH AND KRONOS GOV
oracion: The healthy water awareness group, Wellness for All (WFA), has condemned both GAStech International and the Government of Kronos.
organizaciones: Wellness for All,WFA,GAStech International,the Government of Kronos

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL (WFA) BLASTS GASTECH AND KRONOS GOV
oracion:
WFA's statement claims widespread groundwater contamination, a lack of adequate safeguards, clean-up demands being ignored and no government oversight.

The Government of Kronos, when contacted, declined to comment.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL (WFA) BLASTS GASTECH AND KRONOS GOV
oracion: However, GAStech International's Environmental Safety Advisor Ingmar Casablancas responded to the claims, "The alleged charges levied against GAStech International are unfounded.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL (WFA) BLASTS GASTECH AND KRONOS GOV
oracion: GAStech International and the Government of Kronos cooperate tirelessly to ensure a clean, safe, and prosperous work place.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL (WFA) BLASTS GASTECH AND KRONOS GOV
oracion: We are both devoted to the preservation of the environment."

titulo: KRONOS GDP ON THE RIS
oracion: The real gross domestic product - the output of goods and services produced by labor and property located in Kronos - increased at an annual rate of 5.4% in the fourth quarter of 1999, according to the advance estimate released by the Bureau of Economics.

titulo: KRONOS GDP ON THE RIS
oracion: This marks the 5th year in a row with positive GDP growth for the developing country.

titulo: KRONOS GDP ON THE RIS
oracion: Most of this growth can be contributed to the relationship between the Government of Kronos and GAStech International.

titulo: GASTECH REPORTS RECORD EARNING
oracion: GAStech International, as projected earlier this month, reported record fiscal 1998 profit of $110 million.

titulo: GASTECH REPORTS RECORD EARNING
oracion: GAStech issued a full-year earnings preview February 4 as part of its latest attempts to drown out the accusations of groundwater contamination in Kronos levied by Wellness for All.

titulo: GASTECH REPORTS RECORD EARNING
oracion: The company reported net income of $29.5 million for the fourth quarter.

titulo: GASTECH REPORTS RECORD EARNING
oracion: "GAStech International has delivered another year of superior financial performance achieved through a consistent vision and expert execution," Sten Sanjorge, Jr., GAStech's Chief Executive, said in a brief statement.

titulo: GASTECH REPORTS RECORD EARNING
oracion: Sanjorge, Jr. failed to mention the November 13th statement from Wellness for All blasting the company and its relationship with the Government of Kronos.

titulo: GASTECH REPORTS RECORD EARNING
oracion: However, he did mention the opening of GAStech's new natural gas processing plant is on pace.

titulo: GASTECH'S EXPANSION REACHES THE SHORES OF KRONO
oracion: The groundbreaking today at the Tiskele Bend site marks another flag planted in foreign soil by GAStech International.

titulo: GASTECH'S EXPANSION REACHES THE SHORES OF KRONO
oracion: Sten Sanjorge Jr.'s international expansion has been the hallmark of his brief tenure at the helm following his father's death in February of this year.

titulo: GASTECH'S EXPANSION REACHES THE SHORES OF KRONO
oracion: "Today is great day for the People of Kronos.

titulo: GASTECH'S EXPANSION REACHES THE SHORES OF KRONO
oracion: With the jobs, and the cheaper and cleaner fuel provided by GAStech you can begin to live the lives you deserve."

titulo: GASTECH'S EXPANSION REACHES THE SHORES OF KRONO
oracion: On the heels of GAStech's expansion into Asteria, the Tiskele Bend site has the potential to dwarf any of GAStech's other gas fields.

titulo: GASTECH'S EXPANSION REACHES THE SHORES OF KRONO
oracion: Conservative estimates of preliminary test well results place the Tiskele Bend field at least on par with the largest of GAStech's Tethan fields.

titulo: HUGE IPO MAKES SANJORGE BILLIONAIR
oracion: President and CEO of GAStech International Sten Sanjorge, Jr. can add another description to his name: billionaire.

titulo: HUGE IPO MAKES SANJORGE BILLIONAIR
oracion: And not only a billionaire, nearly a billionaire two times over as GAStech International sold shares in an initial public offering.

titulo: HUGE IPO MAKES SANJORGE BILLIONAIR
oracion: GAStech International, founded in 1961 as Sanjorge Trucking by Sten Sanjorge, Sr., produces about 5 million cubic meters of gas daily at its GAStech - Kronos drilling site Tiskele Bend.

titulo: HUGE IPO MAKES SANJORGE BILLIONAIR
oracion: As for the particulars of the filing: Sanjorge Jr.'s 51% stake in the company is worth $1.96 billion; Beatriz Fluss' (widow of company co-founder Hank Fluss) 33% stake is worth $1.27 billion.

titulo: HUGE IPO MAKES SANJORGE BILLIONAIR
oracion: Don't feel sorry for the GAStech - Kronos executives.

titulo: HUGE IPO MAKES SANJORGE BILLIONAIR
oracion: The filings show that the GAStech - Kronos executives earned a collective $327.25 million from the newly vested shares including $96.25 million each for CFO Ingrid Barranco, CIO Ada Campo-Corrente, and COO Orhan Strum.

titulo: HUGE IPO MAKES SANJORGE BILLIONAIR
oracion: Environmental Safety Advisor Willem Vasco-Pais also earned $38.5 million.

titulo: GASTECH ADOPTS NEW LOG
oracion: With great fanfare GAStech International's President and CEO Sten Sanjorge, Jr. revealed the company's new logo, part of the company's rebranding process.

titulo: GASTECH ADOPTS NEW LOG
oracion: During the press conference Sanjorge, Jr. spoke of the new logo - a tri-part blue flame - that is reminiscent of a leaf to "help position GAStech and its products as a clean fuel alternative."

titulo: GASTECH ADOPTS NEW LOG
oracion: He also referenced that the tri-part flame represents the past, present, and future of the company in that by keeping "one eye on the past we know from where we came - our humble beginnings; one eye on the future we will know where we are going - our coming success; and both feet planted in the present we will be proactive in an ever-changing, competitive industry."

titulo: GASTECH ADOPTS NEW LOG
oracion:
Finally, Sanjorge, Jr. asserted GAStech International's "blue flame is an enduring beacon of environmental responsibility, and a symbol of a clean energy business moving forward." 

This rebranding process and new logo seem to be in response to recent trouble the multi-national gas giant has been struggling with in Kronos including the February 19 protest at GAStech - Kronos' headquarters of 200 people who blocked entrance to the building, resulting in several arrests.

titulo: GASTECH ADOPTS NEW LOG
oracion: The protest and others in and around Abila, the capital of Kronos, have been in response to alleged water contamination issues and a lack of Government and GAStech response.

titulo: GASTECH ADOPTS NEW LOG
oracion: Sten Sanjorge, Jr. declined to comment directly on questions regarding protests and environmental contamination.

titulo: GASTECH ADOPTS NEW LOG
oracion: He deflected, "Today is a great day for GAStech.

titulo: GASTECH ADOPTS NEW LOG
oracion: I won't let the day be derailed by unfounded, borderline libelous, allegations."

titulo: GASTECH SHIFTS FOCUS TO KRONO
oracion: GAStech International has shifted its focus from Tethys to the small Mediterranean island of Kronos and the vast gas deposits beneath the ground.

titulo: GASTECH SHIFTS FOCUS TO KRONO
oracion: Recent charges of groundwater contamination against GAStech International and tightening environmental regulations lead by the Tethan Interior Minister, Ivar Blanes, certainly play into the shifting focus.

titulo: GASTECH SHIFTS FOCUS TO KRONO
oracion: With environmental regulation lax to nonexistent in Kronos and a friendly local government, GAStech's move feels inevitable in hindsight.

titulo: DRILLING TECHNIQUE BANNED IN TETHY
oracion: GAStech International's Hyper Acidic Substrate Removal (HASR) has officially been banned by the Tethys government due to the high probability of water contamination.

titulo: DRILLING TECHNIQUE BANNED IN TETHY
oracion: GAStech developed the innovative drilling technique in 1974 proved quite successful for the extraction of gas, but the technique's environmental impact is deemed unacceptable by the Tethys government due to the high probability of water table contamination from waste products produced during the HASR process.

titulo: DRILLING TECHNIQUE BANNED IN TETHY
oracion: Sten Sanjorge, Jr. responded to the ban saying, "So be it.

titulo: DRILLING TECHNIQUE BANNED IN TETHY
oracion: Tethys' loss will be another country's gain."

titulo: RANSOM DEMANDS MADE IN GASTECH KIDNAPPIN
oracion: The Protectors of Kronos have not only taken responsibility for the kidnapping of GAStech International employees, but have also made a ransom demand of $20M from the President and CEO Sten Sanjorge, Jr.

titulo: RANSOM DEMANDS MADE IN GASTECH KIDNAPPIN
oracion: As reported yesterday, it was speculated that Sanjorge, Jr. was the target of the kidnapping; however, Sanjorge, Jr. is safe back in Tethys.

titulo: RANSOM DEMANDS MADE IN GASTECH KIDNAPPIN
oracion: The kidnapping group, The Protectors of Kronos, was founded in 1998 in Elodis, a rural township outside of the capital Abila.

titulo: RANSOM DEMANDS MADE IN GASTECH KIDNAPPIN
oracion: They have been protesting for clean water, human rights, and against the corruption of the Government of Kronos and GAStech International.

titulo: RANSOM DEMANDS MADE IN GASTECH KIDNAPPIN
oracion: They have become increasingly violent with their protests devolving into riots, fire bombings, vandalism, and looting.

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: An explosion at a nearby gas drilling well pad woke Rebecca Cato around 3 a.m. on Sunday morning.

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: When she left her home in Elodis, Kronos - a rural township outside the capital Abila - to investigate the noise she noticed a large fire coming from GAStech International's Tiskele Bend site.

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: The GAStech-owned well near Elodis ignited methane gas underground causing a fire that lasted for around an hour.

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: At least four GAStech employees appeared to have been taken away by ambulance; however, GAStech has declined to comment on the extent and nature of their injuries.

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: GAStech's CEO Sten Sanjorge Jr. downplayed the event stating, "This event could hardly be described as an explosion," but merely a common practice referred to as flaring.

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: He continued, "I won't bore you with the details, but a temporary flare is often used during well production testing."

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: Mrs. Cato and other locals from Elodis were turned away by GAStech employees and government officials.

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: Eventually, locals downriver were evacuated.

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: Rebecca Cato said, "After sending us away without a single question answered, they came to our doors and told us to leave our homes.

titulo: EXPLOSION ROCKS GASTECH'S TISKELE BEND SIT
oracion: It was the middle of the night where was I to go."

titulo: GRAND OPENING GASTEC
oracion: TITLE: GRAND OPENING GASTECH-KRONOS

titulo: GRAND OPENING GASTEC
oracion: PUBLISHED: 10 October 1995

titulo: GRAND OPENING GASTEC
oracion: With his trademark flash, Sten Sanjorge, Jr. President of GAStech International opened the new GAStech-Kronos headquarters.

titulo: GRAND OPENING GASTEC
oracion: The ribbon was cut with a huge pair of scissors, matched in size only by Sanjorge Jr.'s smile.

titulo: GRAND OPENING GASTEC
oracion: The 50 million dollar price tag for the new headquarters is just a drop in the bucket for GAStech.

titulo: GRAND OPENING GASTEC
oracion: The gas field in production outside of Abila has exceeded even Sanjorge's oversized expectations, paying for the building many times over.

titulo: GRAND OPENING GASTEC
oracion: Present at the ribbon cutting ceremony were several representatives from the Kronos Government.

titulo: SANJORGE JR. TAKING GASTECH INTERNATIONAL PUBLI
oracion: After 52 years of being privately owned, Sten Sanjorge, Jr. is taking the natural gas exploration and production company GAStech International public.

titulo: SANJORGE JR. TAKING GASTECH INTERNATIONAL PUBLI
oracion: With an eye toward becoming even more of a world player in the gas industry, Sanjorge, Jr. is going public to generate working capital for further international expansion and exploration.

titulo: SANJORGE JR. TAKING GASTECH INTERNATIONAL PUBLI
oracion: The company, founded in 1961 by Sten Sanjorge, Sr., said Monday it plans a stock offering that could place its value in the neighborhood of $3.75 billion.

titulo: SANJORGE JR. TAKING GASTECH INTERNATIONAL PUBLI
oracion: The IPO is expected before the end of the year.

titulo: LANDSLIDE VICTORY FOR PRESIDENT KAPELOU
oracion: The people of Kronos have overwhelmingly elected new President Dorel Kapelou II.

titulo: LANDSLIDE VICTORY FOR PRESIDENT KAPELOU
oracion: Former President Luis Araullo conceded defeat yesterday when early returns came in strong for Kapelou II.

titulo: LANDSLIDE VICTORY FOR PRESIDENT KAPELOU
oracion: The results for the 1 October election are as follows: Dorel Kapelou II elected with 62% of the vote and Luis Araullo receiving just 36% of the vote.

titulo: LANDSLIDE VICTORY FOR PRESIDENT KAPELOU
oracion: A resounding victory for the new elected President and a clear mandate for Kapelou's vision for the country.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: Protesters aligned with the Protectors of Kronos (POK) activist group surrounded government buildings chanting and carry images of their so-called martyrs.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: Kronos government security forces in concert with Abila police suppressed the protest with an impressive show of force.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: Dressed in black the authorities donning helmets and gasmasks and brandishing riot shields, fired tear gas canisters as the protesters refused to disperse after several warnings.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: The group gathered proved reluctant to disperse even after the tear gas and the authorities pressed into the group protecting themselves with their shields and freely swinging their batons.

titulo: GOVERNMENT RESPONDS TO ANOTHER ROUND OF PROTESTS
oracion: The remaining protesters were surrounded by the riot police and after repeated baton blows many were dragged away under arrest.

titulo: GOVERNMENT CITES 'MINOR' CONTAMINATION NEAR ELODIS
oracion: After continued complaints and appeals from the people of Elodis government officials acknowledge minor contamination in and around the rural township in a report on their investigation into the townspeople's health issues.

titulo: GOVERNMENT CITES 'MINOR' CONTAMINATION NEAR ELODIS
oracion: However, the government report stops short of blaming GAStech International and its Tiskele Bend site 20 km upstream as the people of Elodis assert.

titulo: GOVERNMENT CITES 'MINOR' CONTAMINATION NEAR ELODIS
oracion: The government report cites no root cause or causes can be determined at this time with more research and investigations needed.

titulo: GOVERNMENT CITES 'MINOR' CONTAMINATION NEAR ELODIS
oracion: Though the report admits some contamination it goes on the qualify the level stating, "The minor level of contamination is well within international health standards agreed upon by the Government of Kronos and GAStech International as negotiated in the Tiskele Bend site contract."

titulo: POSSIBLE CONTAMINATION IN ELODIS
oracion: About 25 km West of Abila is the small rural township of Elodis, situated on the Tiskele River.

titulo: POSSIBLE CONTAMINATION IN ELODIS
oracion: Roughly 20 km upstream is the Tiskele Bend site operated by GAStech International on government-owned land.

titulo: POSSIBLE CONTAMINATION IN ELODIS
oracion: Townspeople claim the site is contaminating the land and water making their people sick.

titulo: POSSIBLE CONTAMINATION IN ELODIS
oracion: In a statement the government of Kronos has denied that the Tiskele Bend site is the source of any contamination insisting that both "natural gas and the drilling process are clean."

titulo: POSSIBLE CONTAMINATION IN ELODIS
oracion: The statement continued, "If our people are sick we will help them get well.

titulo: POSSIBLE CONTAMINATION IN ELODIS
oracion: That is the duty of government: to protect its people."

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASED
oracion: For roughly 6 hours GAStech - Kronos employee Edvard Vann was interrogated by Kronos Police and Government officials before being released at 17:00 this evening.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASED
oracion: The apparent confusion stems from the similarity between his name and that of a Protector of Kronos member.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASED
oracion: Vann, a security guard for GAStech, was furious, stating, "I have nothing to do whatsoever with any members of the terrorist group POK.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASED
oracion: I was born here in Abila and I support my government and my president.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASED
oracion: Being accused and being interrogated for 6 hours as a terrorist POK member is one of the worst days of my life.

titulo: GASTECH EMPLOYEE INTERROGATED, RELEASED
oracion: With some 14 GAStech employees still unaccounted for, one cannot blame the police or the government for not leaving any stone unturned.

titulo: MEETING SET FOR TOMORROW MORNING
oracion: With a meeting set tomorrow at 8 AM, the recent Initial Public Offering, and CEO Sten Sanjorge, Jr. in town reporters will be descending on the GAStech - Kronos headquarters in droves with plenty of questions. and his GAStech - Kronos leadership group to comment on the IPO, their recent windfalls, and GAStech's plans for Kronos.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSING
oracion: Miriam Avila, an administrative assistant at GAStech International, has confirmed that members of the GAStech leadership are in fact missing.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSING
oracion: The group was expected to arrive at the Government reception following this morning's meeting at GAStech - Kronos headquarters, but never showed up.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSING
oracion: Avila denied that any GAStech employee has been abducted.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSING
oracion: The GAStech - Kronos leadership was also handsomely rewarded.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSING
oracion: The IPO filings show that the executive group earned a collective $327.25 million from the newly vested shares including $96.25 million each for CFO Ingrid Barranco, CIO Ada Campo-Corrente, and COO Orhan Strum.

titulo: GASTECH LEADERSHIP CONFIRMED MISSING

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: ABILA, Kronos -

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: With the third anniversary of Elian Karel's death approaching - former member of the Protectors of Kronos - the question is: who are the protesters?

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The Protectors of Kronos or POK were founded in 1997 by residents of rural Elodis on the advice of the now defunct Wellness for All (WFA), an international water safety group.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK was initiated to bring attention to the clean water issues surrounding Elodis to the Government of Kronos and the world.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK asserts that GAStech International's Tiskele Bend natural gas drilling site is the source of both the contamination of drinking water as well as the destruction of the traditional farmland surrounding Elodis.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: However, with the fragmenting of WFA due to funding issues, the POK's demands were largely ignored and downplayed.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The Government of Kronos officially refuted the claim citing the fragmentation of the WFA organization as evidence of an unreliable source not to be trusted.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: Regardless, Juliana became the POK's first martyr and has used Juliana's image on campaign literature ever since.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK's second major martyr is Elian Karel, who died in 2009 while incarcerated of undetermined causes.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK asserts he was arrested on trumped up charges while the Government of Kronos contends he was a radical and violent activist engaged in tax evasion.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: Karel had been involved with the POK since its inception given that his father, Jeroen Karel, was an original member.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: The POK has evolved from peaceful protests and demonstrations demanding government action to more violent activities including riots as they claim that the government has done little to nothing in addressing the contamination, poisonings, and deaths suffered by their people.

titulo: WHO ARE THE PROTESTERS
oracion: As of 2011, the Government of Kronos has labeled the POK as a "public threat".

titulo: BRAZEN DAY TIME ASSAULT BY POK
oracion: ABILA, Kronos -

titulo: BRAZEN DAY TIME ASSAULT BY POK
oracion: The brazen day time assault on two peace officers by the POK is just another violent, terroristic act in a long string of such acts.

titulo: BRAZEN DAY TIME ASSAULT BY POK
oracion:
Police spokesman Adrien Carman said of the attack, "Assaulting a police officer and destroying government property are serious crimes. 

Further exacerbating the situation, the two criminals defaced the officers' car by spray painting the POK logo.

titulo: BRAZEN DAY TIME ASSAULT BY POK
oracion: If they can attack two police officers in broad daylight, who is next?

titulo: WRAP UP OF EVENTS AT GASTECH
oracion: A long tense day of conflicting reports and confusing information has come to an end.

titulo: WRAP UP OF EVENTS AT GASTECH
oracion: What we know for certain is that 14 GAStech employees are not only missing, but kidnapped as confirmed by a Kronos Government source.

titulo: WRAP UP OF EVENTS AT GASTECH
oracion: At this time it is unclear who the missing are and whether they are citizens of Kronos of Tethys, as many GAStech employees are Tethan.

titulo: WRAP UP OF EVENTS AT GASTECH
oracion: Speculation about the motives of the kidnappers has been rampant due to the recent news of the GAStech Initial Public Offering only a month ago.

titulo: WRAP UP OF EVENTS AT GASTECH
oracion: Edvard Vann, a GAStech Kronos security guard who was interrogated and released after 6 hours, gave the indication that the Protectors of Kronos were involved or at least suspected as being the perpetrators behind today's events.

titulo: WRAP UP OF EVENTS AT GASTECH
oracion: A GAStech International senior security executive has been on site to support the investigation aiding the Abila Police Department and Kronos Government officials.

titulo: WRAP UP OF EVENTS AT GASTECH
oracion: Shortly after the morning meeting ended at 10:00, Abila Fire Department trucks responded to reports of a fire at the GAStech office.

titulo: TISKELE BEND EXPLOSION AND FIRE
oracion: A spark at the GAStech International-owned well at the Tiskele Bend site ignited methane gas several hundred feet underground, causing a fireball and fire that burned for about an hour is the findings from a dual GAStech - government investigation of the explosion and subsequent fire Sunday morning.

titulo: TISKELE BEND EXPLOSION AND FIRE
oracion: Four GAStech employees suffered injuries including minor burns and broken bones.

titulo: TISKELE BEND EXPLOSION AND FIRE
oracion: No local residents were injured as well and though some residents of Elodis were evacuated from their homes the investigation indicates that the evacuation was unnecessary.

titulo: TISKELE BEND EXPLOSION AND FIRE
oracion: While the official cause of the explosion is still under investigation, the problem may have come from a defect in the wellhead itself.

titulo: TISKELE BEND EXPLOSION AND FIRE
oracion: GAStech's wellheads are ringed with collars that have set pins running through them.

titulo: TRAFFIC ACCIDENT NEAR ELODIS
oracion: A government investigation has concluded a traffic accident involving a GAStech International vehicle and the vehicle of a family from Elodis resulting in the deaths of the four family members was the result of driver error on the part of the Elodisian driver.

titulo: TRAFFIC ACCIDENT NEAR ELODIS
oracion: Government spokesman Rufus Drymiau said that the investigation found the deadly accident was triggered when the driver from Elodis crossed over into oncoming traffic.

titulo: TRAFFIC ACCIDENT NEAR ELODIS
oracion: Three occupants  - Valeria Edris, Celia Edris, and Marcellus Edris - died at the scene.

titulo: TRAFFIC ACCIDENT NEAR ELODIS
oracion: Carmine Edris, 9, was found wandering around the accident site and died later of his injuries.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL ISSUES STATEMENT ON ELODIS
oracion: The international healthy water awareness group Wellness for All (WFA) have performed testing on the local water in Elodis finding high level of hazardous materials in residential water wells.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL ISSUES STATEMENT ON ELODIS
oracion: In a statement released by WFA, the group directs blame to the Government of Kronos and GAStech International, a natural gas company from Tethys.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL ISSUES STATEMENT ON ELODIS
oracion: In addition to directing blame WFA also demands that the two clean up the contamination, which includes high levels of benzene, toluene and xylene arsenic, barium, chromium, lead and selenium.

titulo: WELLNESS FOR ALL ISSUES STATEMENT ON ELODIS
oracion: Additionally, WFA has been working with the activist group Protectors of Kronos to lobby the government to apply pressure.

Michale Kraft, Karel's lawyer, released a statement asserting that the charges leveled against his client were "false" and that he hoped his client "would be released [from police custody] by week's end." 

Police spokesman Adrien Carman responded the statement by Kraft, stating, "I think Mr. Kraft has underestimated the seriousness of his client's situation. 

Just last month, Karel's group was responsible for the trespassing incident that blocked entrance to the GAStech - Kronos headquarters.

oracion: A POK rally designed to bring attention to claims of environmental damage have done more damage to their image.

titulo: GASTECH HEADQUARTERS BLOCKED BY POK
oracion: The rally outside of GAStech International's headquarters resulted in multiple arrests for trespassing.

titulo: GASTECH HEADQUARTERS BLOCKED BY POK
oracion: About two hundred people gathered in front of the GAStech building chanting slogans and waving signs that held the visages of people who have allegedly died due to environmental contamination.

titulo: GASTECH HEADQUARTERS BLOCKED BY POK
oracion: Ten of the protestors chained themselves to the doors of the building in an attempt to prevent GAStech employees from going to work.

titulo: GASTECH HEADQUARTERS BLOCKED BY POK
oracion: Police spokesman Adrien Carman said, "We allowed the group some latitude with their rally, but when GAStech complained that the protestors were blocking entrance to their building, we had to take action.

titulo: GASTECH HEADQUARTERS BLOCKED BY POK
oracion: The last thing we wanted to happen was for a GAStech employee to get hurt by the crowd just because he was trying to go to work."

oracion:
Protests erupted around the Kronos government buildings, downtown, and elsewhere around Abila eventually escalating into riots and violence.  

The activists are protesting the death yesterday of Elian Karel, a Protector of Kronos (POK) activist who died in jail after being arrested for tax evasion.

oracion: A general sense of chaos broke out with chanting protesters, fires, and fleeing citizens.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: The world of gas is distant, difficult and far flung.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: In Tethys a few years ago, I journeyed laboriously to the remote gas fields of Tethys to look at a contentious new energy producing area.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: One of the sites I visited was a local office of the Sanjorge Gas company, crammed with reinforced work boots and overalls and the chemicals and supplies you need to run a gas operation.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: But I'd forgotten about the encounter until I went back to Tethys the other day for the first time since their early years, to reacquaint with the man who created the business, Sten Sanjorge: one man (one of the richest individuals in Tethys) who has lived through the whole story of gas prospecting and prospered mightily from it.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: But as I went round the capital city of Centrum interviewing people, I soon realised that this was not just a story of new energy.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: Something very significant has happened to turn Centrum into a global centre of gas industry expertise.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: It then seemed a pretty impossible dream, turning an island of coal into a place with abundant oil and gas supplies.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion:
It seemed to us on the west coast of Scotland that the far flung city of Centrum, Tethys was getting a bit big for its boots, starting to believe in a new fantasy industry. 

By the early 1970s, a new gas company, GAStech, began its juggernaut-like advances.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: Under his canny guidance, GAStech evolved into a major supplier of natural gas to the local region, and then much further afield.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: You notice them in the constant clutter of helicopters to-ing and fro-ing out to remote areas, and the planes lined up at the city's airport to shuttle execs back and forth from the city.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: But Sanjorge has just been asked to produce a report for the Tethan government recommending the best ways of ensuring that Tethys continues to produce energy for decades to come.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: The easy-to-get stuff has been produced, so keeping the gas coming will need much investment and more clever new techniques, such as the hyper-acidic substrate removal techniques developed by the company in 1974.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: So thanks to clever people such as Sten Sanjorge and the people who work with him, Centrum has achieved what every place where raw materials are discovered longs to do.

titulo: Centrum's central role in the Tethan Gas Industry
oracion: The city has taken the temporary boon of energy on its doorstep, and turned it into specialized knowledge and intellectual property which may make Centrum a centre of gas expertise long after the gas itself runs out.

titulo: Profile:  Elian Karel
oracion:
<<deleted image of Elian Karel speaking at a rally in Abila>> 

Voice of protest for some, popularist demagogue for others, Protectors of Kronos leader Elian Karel became a martyr and a rallying point for some; a figure of disdain and rabblerousing for others, and a political concern to the Kronosian government, within an event filled year, accented by his suspicious death on Friday.

titulo: Profile:  Elian Karel
oracion: The leader of a forbearant environmental activist group, Karel had started a brand of politics all his own, that propelled the POK into the spotlight of this island nation.

titulo: Profile:  Elian Karel
oracion: Fueled by a growing dissatisfaction with the heavy-handed Kronosian government, he started driving the POK into an action-based organization, instead of one waiting for their government to make things aright.

titulo: Profile:  Elian Karel
oracion: Resurrecting the embers of the Juliana Vann campaign, the 10 year old girl who died from illnesses attributed to the government-favored GASTech corporation's industrial waste streams in 1998, Karel was arrested and thrown in jail following a POK-initiated human roadblock in front of GAStech headquarters in May.

titulo: Profile:  Elian Karel
oracion: Karel died Wednesday while serving time in jail.

titulo: Profile:  Elian Karel
oracion: Rather charismatic, Karel was able to inspire a crowd and draw attention to the POK social and political agenda.

titulo: Profile:  Elian Karel
oracion: likened the POK to a terrorist group in a press interview, Karel  quipped, "Sanjorge is a brilliant leader of GAStech."

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: It is the biggest company in Kronos, the third largest gas company on the planet, and it is fifty-three years old.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: In the past it has had a reputation as corrupt and environmentally harmful, but nowadays GAStech, the former Tethys-only business, is trying to earn the trust of international investors.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: It is an uphill task, and there is no certainty that Gastech has the ability to convince potential investors it has mended its ways, and is no longer rooted in the eco-hostile past.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: GAStech's pipeline operations are based in eastern Kronos, and there is close relationship with the Kronosian government.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: This is the heart of Kronos's pipeline business, where gas from the eastern gas fields is piped west towards the rest of Kronos, Tethys and Europe.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: GAStech does more than just pump gas.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: The head of GAStech, Sten Sanjorge, Jr, whose photo stares out from calendars and picture frames everywhere in the country, acknowledges the "state within a state" accusations, but argues that the company simply needs to look after its workers and the communities around them.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: The GAStech empire owns 2 thousand cows and 3 thousand pigs in its company farms, runs gyms, and offers subsidised holidays in Black Sea resorts for key employees.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: There is an argument, however, that the energy business is different from other industries, requiring energy corporations to operate in distinct ways.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: Working in far-off places with no previous infrastructure means oil and gas sites will always be, to some extent, company towns.

titulo: GAStech Profile
oracion: GAStech certainly strives to ensure its employees can move in and out of these locations by operating a private fleet of four planes to ferry its staff the huge distances between sites.

titulo: Multi-Country Task Force Forme
oracion: Interpol has announced the formation of a new multi-country task force to combat the increasingly wide distribution of the drug methyldimethyl cathinone (MDMC).

titulo: Multi-Country Task Force Forme
oracion: Heading the task force is Senior Inspector Robert Loblaw, a veteran officer who led the very successful Tethys Counterdrug Team.

titulo: Multi-Country Task Force Forme
oracion:
"These designer drugs have certain clues as to their origin," Loblaw stated in an interview. 

This particular blend of the drug MDMC, also known by its street names "cotton candy", "spice dreams" and "Tulip Blossom", was found previously only in Asteria but has made its way to the streets of Tethys and other international countries. 

The Asterian People's Army (APA) is a paramilitary organization which has been engaged in terrorist activities funded through its criminal enterprises, which include drug trafficking.

titulo: Multi-Country Task Force Forme
oracion: In recent years the APA has sought to build their brand through websites and the publication of a professional, high-quality magazine called "Arise".

titulo: Multi-Country Task Force Forme

titulo: Multi-Country Task Force Forme
oracion: "An increase in mental health problems, including hallucinations and paranoia, accompanied by violent behavior and a marked increase in suicide rates are only a few of the indicators of the usage of this designer drug."

Aid agencies have warned that the monetary and food needs have increased worldwide and that they may not be able to meet basic needs. 

The UN Office for Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs says that 15 million people remain in need of vital goods and services, because the number and severity of crises has resulted in a lack of "food, healthcare, and access to livelihoods."
